F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fgaming%2Fnews%2Fformer-pixar-animator-colin-brady-launches-bunny-based-ip-via-amgi-studios-epic-games-amazon-prime-gaminb-1235730652%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fgaming%2Fnews%2Fformer-pixar-animator-colin-brady-launches-bunny-based-ip-via-amgi-studios-epic-games-amazon-prime-gaminb-1235730652%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Crude%20Oil%20Imports%20Fell%20to%2010-Month%20Low%20in%20August%20Due%20to%20Production%20Cuts%20by%20Russia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04193929%2Fimage-966.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20crude%20oil%20imports%20declined%20to%20a%2010-month%20low%20in%20August%2C%20primarily%20due%20to%20production%20cuts%20by%20Russia%20and%20autumn%20refinery%20maintenance.%20The%2018.73%20million%20tonnes%20of%20imports%20in%20August%20is%204%25%20lower%20than%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20imports%20in%20August%20were%20the%20lowest%20since%20November%202022.%20However%2C%20imports%20last%20month%20were%20higher%20on%20an%20annual%20basis%20by%206%25%20in%20comparison%20to%20August%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fcompanies%2Findias-crude-oil-imports-slip-to-10-month-low-in-august-2023%2Farticle67327160.ece%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Line%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Petroleum%20Planning%20and%20Analysis%20Cell%20(PPAC)%20said%20the%20imports%20fell%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20month%20in%20August%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cvoluntary%20production%20cuts%20by%20Russia%E2%80%9D%2C%20also%20impacting%20its%20most%20sought-after%20medium%20sour%20grade%20Ural.%20Ural%20imports%20from%20Russia%20to%20India%20in%20August%20slipped%20to%20their%20lowest%20levels%20since%20January%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reduction%20in%20imports%2C%20traders%20in%20India%20say%2C%20is%20due%20to%20smaller%20discounts%20on%20the%20Urals%20grade%20and%20the%20decreased%20appetite%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Indian%20refiners%20owing%20to%20planned%20autumn%20maintenance%20at%20some%20refineries.%20It%20is%20also%20due%20to%20reduced%20domestic%20demand%20in%20the%20country%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20rainy%20season%20until%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20dip%20in%20imports%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20monthly%20bill%20on%20crude%20oil%20rose%2C%20from%20%2410.3%20billion%20in%20July%20to%20%2410.9%20billion%20in%20August%20given%20that%20production%20cuts%20by%20Russia%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20hiked%20global%20crude%20prices.%20However%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20import%20bill%20in%20August%20was%20lower%20on%20an%20annual%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%20this%20year%2C%20Brent%20Crude%20was%20sold%20at%20an%20average%20of%20%2486.22%20per%20barrel%20in%20the%20global%20market%20compared%20to%20%2480.05%20in%20July%202023%20and%20%2499.99%20per%20barrel%20in%20August%202022.%20As%20for%20India%2C%20the%20basket%20crude%20price%20was%20averaged%20at%20%2486.43%20per%20barrel%20in%20August%202023%20against%20%2480.37%20during%20July%202023%20and%20%2497.40%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Energy%20Agency%20(IEA)%20noted%20that%20the%20shipments%20to%20China%20and%20India%20dipped%20to%203.9%20million%20barrels%20per%20day%20in%20August%202023%20from%204.7%20mb%2Fd%20in%20April%20and%20May%202023%20but%20accounted%20for%20more%20than%20half%20the%20total%20volumes.%20It%20also%20observed%20that%C2%A0the%20top%20two%20crude%20oil%20consumers%20globally%20accounted%20for%2080%25%20of%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20total%20exports%20during%20May-July%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20senior%20oil%20marketing%20executive%2C%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Line%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20oil%20in%20the%20upcoming%20festive%20season%2C%20October-December%2C%20would%20spike%20owing%20to%20increased%20industrial%2C%20mining%2C%20construction%2C%20and%20farm%20activity.%20The%20official%20also%20said%20preparations%20for%20the%20festival%20season%20by%20firms%20in%20the%20fast-moving%20consumer%20goods%20(FMCG)%20and%20fast-moving%20consumer%20durables%20(FMCD)%20industry%20could%20also%20increase%20the%20demand%20for%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695283223000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04193929%2Fimage-966.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Findias-crude-oil-imports-fall-to-10-month-low-in-august-due-to-production-cuts-by-russia%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20imports%20in%20August%20were%20the%20lowest%20since%20November%202022%20due%20to%20autumn%20refinery%20maintenance%20by%20Russia.%20India's%20monthly%20bill%20on%20crude%20oil%2C%20however%2C%20rose%20from%20%2410.3%20billion%20in%20July%20to%20%2410.9%20billion%20in%20August.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Findias-crude-oil-imports-fall-to-10-month-low-in-august-due-to-production-cuts-by-russia%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCentre%20Accepts...%26quot%3B%3A%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister's%20Jibe%20On%20NEET%20Zero%20Cut-Off%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20U-turn%20of%20sorts%20the%20Medical%20Counselling%20Committee%20(MCC)%20has%20reduced%20the%20qualifying%20NEET%20percentile%20for%20post%20graduate%20medical%20admission%20to%20zero.%20An%20official%20communication%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20qualifying%20percentile%20for%20PG%20courses%20(Medical%2F%20Dental)%20for%20NEET%20PG%20Counselling%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20Zero%20across%20all%20categories%20by%20MoHFW%26quot%3B.%20It%20added%20%26quot%3BFresh%20registration%20and%20choice%20filling%20for%20Round%203%20of%20PG%20Counselling%20will%20be%20opened%20again%20for%20candidates%20who%20have%20become%20eligible%20after%20reduction%20of%20percentile%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20around%201300%20PG%20Medical%20seats%20remained%20unfilled%20across%20the%20country.%20While%20this%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20fill%20up%20seats%20in%20private%20medical%20colleges%2C%20largely%20run%20by%20politicians%20%C2%A0which%20charge%20around%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20a%20year%20for%20the%20masters%20programmes%2C%20many%20express%20concerns%20that%20this%20would%20pave%20way%20for%20deterioration%20of%20quality%20of%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fneet-pg-2023-cut-off-percentile-reduced-to-zero-across-categories-4407124%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20NEET-PG%202023%20Cut-Off%20Percentile%20Reduced%20To%20Zero%20Across%20Categories%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMarkandeyan%20(name%20changed)%20a%20senior%20doctor%20and%20a%20parent%20of%20a%20PG%20medical%20aspirant%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20means%20it%20is%20now%20possible%20for%20a%20low%20scoring%20student%20in%20plus%20two%20exam%2C%20score%20an%20abysmally%20low%20score%20on%20undergraduate%20NEET%20and%20still%20gain%20admission%20to%20MS%20or%20MD%20scoring%20zero%20on%20PG%20NEET.%20Imagine%20the%20quality%20of%20doctors%20India%20would%20produce.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20state%20that%20opposes%20NEET%2C%20arguing%20it%20favours%20only%20affluent%20students%20who%20can%20afford%20private%20coaching%20and%20works%20against%20poor%20and%20rural%20students%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20M%20K%20Stalin%20called%20the%20development%20a%20confession%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20that%20%26quot%3BCentre%20accepts%20benefit%20of%20NEET%20is%20zero%26quot%3B.%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BBy%20reducing%20NEET%20PG%20cut%20off%20to%20zero%2C%20Union%20government%20accepts%20that%20NEET%20is%20meaningless.%20It%20is%20just%20about%20coaching%20centres%20and%20paying%20for%20the%20exam.%20NEET%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20merit%2C%20we%20have%20been%20saying%20all%20along%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20had%20abolished%20entrance%20test%20for%20undergraduate%20%C2%A0medical%20admission%20and%20made%20MBBS%20admissions%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20Class%2012%20marks.%20During%20the%20UPA%20regime%20former%20president%20Kalam%20had%20given%20assent%20to%20the%20state%20to%20be%20exempted%20from%20NEET.%20Presently%20though%20the%20state%20assembly%20had%20passed%20a%20bill%20seeing%20exemption%2C%20President%20Murmu%20is%20yet%20to%20give%20assent.%20The%20Centre%20is%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20criticism%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695283200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F08fub0b8_mk-stalin-1200_625x300_16_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcentre-accepts-tamil-nadu-chief-minister-mk-stalins-jibe-on-neet-zero-cut-off-4409824%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Centre%20reduces%20NEET%20cut%20off%20to%20zero%20for%20PG%20medical%20admission.%20M%20K%20Stalin%20says%20the%20decision%20vindicates%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20stand%20against%20NEET.%20For%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C%20the%20state%20had%20abolished%20entrance%20test%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20admission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcentre-accepts-tamil-nadu-chief-minister-mk-stalins-jibe-on-neet-zero-cut-off-4409824%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hunger%20%E2%80%98Shocking%20Stain%20on%20Humanity%2C%20Epic%20Human%20Rights%20Violation%E2%80%99%3A%20UN's%20Guterres%20at%20SDG%20Summit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21131157%2FGuterres.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EUnited%20Nations%C2%A0Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20on%20Monday%20told%20those%20present%20in%20New%20York%20for%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fun-sustainable-development-goals-losing-the-race%2Fa-66879154%5C%22%3ESustainable%20Development%20Goals%C2%A0summit%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20that%20the%20world%20needs%20a%20%E2%80%9Cglobal%20rescue%20plan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20text%20of%20commitment%20to%20the%2017%C2%A0Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs)%20%E2%80%93%20which%20relate%20to%20almost%20all%20aspects%20of%20politics%20and%20livelihood%20and%20are%20primarily%20aimed%20at%20ending%20extreme%20poverty%20and%20hunger%20%E2%80%93%20was%20passed%20unanimously%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUN%20member%20states%20adopted%20the%20SDGs%20in%202015%2C%20committing%20at%20the%20time%20to%20achieving%20them%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%202023%20summit%2C%20a%20group%20of%20nations%20led%20by%20Russia%20had%20vowed%20to%20block%20passages%20but%20ultimately%20dropped%20the%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fantonio-guterres%2Ft-41524150%5C%22%3ESecretary-general%20Guterres%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20only%20about%2015%25%20of%20the%20goals%20%E2%80%93%20from%20eliminating%20extreme%20poverty%20and%20malnutrition%2C%20improving%20education%20and%20health%20provision%2C%20providing%20clean%20water%20and%20sanitation%20to%20all%2C%20and%20ensuring%20access%20to%20decent%20work%20and%20economic%20growth%20%E2%80%93%20are%20on%20track%20and%20warned%20that%20in%20some%20cases%20there%20had%20even%20been%20backsliding.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20chief%C2%A0said%3A%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThe%20SDGs%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20list%20of%20goals.%20They%20carry%20the%20hopes%2C%20dreams%2C%20rights%20and%20expectations%20of%20people%20everywhere.%20In%20our%20world%20of%20plenty%2C%20hunger%20is%20a%20shocking%20stain%20on%20humanity%C2%A0and%20an%20epic%20human%20rights%20violation.%20It%20is%20an%20indictment%20of%20every%20one%20of%20us%20that%20millions%20of%20people%20are%20starving%20in%20this%20day%20and%20age.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGerman%20Chancellor%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Folaf-scholz%2Ft-57304267%5C%22%3EOlaf%20Scholz%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0bemoaned%20the%C2%A0lack%20of%20progress%20and%20told%20those%20gathered%20Monday%C2%A0that%20developing%20countries%20expected%20support%20from%20wealthier%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProgress%20on%20many%20SDGs%20%E2%80%98stagnant%20or%20rolling%20backwards%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20the%20difficulty%20of%20meeting%20such%20lofty%20goals%2C%20Laurel%20Patterson%2C%20spokesperson%C2%A0for%C2%A0the%20United%20Nations%20Development%20Programme%2C%20echoed%20Guterres%E2%80%99%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CProgress%2C%20as%20you%E2%80%99re%20seeing%20across%20the%20board%2C%20is%20certainly%20not%20where%20we%20expected%20it%20to%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20Patterson%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20cases%20%5Bit%20is%5D%20stagnant%20and%20rolling%20backwards.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20she%20claimed%20the%20SDGs%20remained%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20best%20opportunity%20for%20us%20as%20a%20global%20community%20to%20move%20forward.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPatterson%20pointed%20to%20poor%20nations%20spending%20more%20than%20twice%20as%20much%20of%20their%20budgets%20on%20servicing%20debt%20than%20on%20social%20welfare%20as%20an%20argument%20for%20debt%20cancellation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%20when%20%E2%80%9Cfiscal%20space%20is%20incredibly%20constrained%E2%80%9D%2C%20issues%20like%20climate%20change%20get%20pitted%20against%20poverty%20relief%2C%20for%20instance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20she%20struck%20a%20strong%20note%20of%20caution%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20what%20development%20looks%20like%20and%20how%20progress%20is%20measured.%20For%20example%2C%20when%20electrification%20spreads%2C%20she%20said%2C%20so%20does%20energy%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20what%20comes%20across%20all%20of%20our%20reports%20%E2%80%93%2072%20out%20of%20the%2095%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20is%20that%20carbon%20emissions%20are%20moving%20in%20the%20wrong%20direction.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20actually%20increased%20since%202019%20and%20these%20are%20indeed%20troubling%20patterns.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20numbers%20and%20current%20trajectories%2C%20Patterson%20remains%20optimistic%20about%20the%20prospects%20of%20progress%20in%20New%20York%2C%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20combination%20of%20choices%2C%20leadership%2C%20political%20will%20and%20investment%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20within%20our%20hands.%20Those%20are%20choices%20that%20are%20possible%20for%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20representatives%20from%20many%20of%20the%20193%20countries%20in%20New%20York%20to%20attend%20the%20General%20Assembly%20%E2%80%93%20which%20formally%20begins%20Tuesday%20and%20lasts%20one%20week%20%E2%80%93%20South%20African%20President%20Cyril%20Ramaphosa%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20indictment%20of%20every%20one%20of%20us%20that%20millions%20of%20people%20are%20starving%20in%20this%20day%20and%20age.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20achievement%20of%20the%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20depends%20on%20the%20fundamental%20reform%20of%20global%20social%2C%20economic%20and%20political%20relations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Funs-guterres-hunger-is-an-epic-human-rights-violation%2Fa-66849579%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fdw.com%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695282614000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21131157%2FGuterres.png%22%2C%22