ndiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103831036.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVishal%20Bharadwaj%20shares%20what%20made%20him%20make%20his%20debut%20as%20an%20OTT%20director%20with%20Charlie%20Chopra%2C%20his%20memories%20of%20Irrfan%20Khan%20and%20long%20association%20with%20Gulzar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvishal-bharadwaj-i-get-disturbed-by-the-mere-thought-of-irrfan-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F103831036.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What's%20Five%20Eyes%20Alliance%20And%20What%20It%20Said%20On%20Khalistani%20Terrorist%20Killing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20accusing%20%26quot%3BIndian%20agents%26quot%3B%20of%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20June%20-%20and%20plunging%20diplomatic%20ties%20with%20India%20to%20a%20new%20low%20-%20one%20of%20the%20key%20quarters%20Canada%20was%20hoping%20for%20support%20from%20is%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20intelligence%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Five%20Eyes%20is%20an%20alliance%20of%20the%20intelligence%20agencies%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Australia%2C%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Canada.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20Washington%20Post%2C%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar%20was%20raised%20privately%20by%20officials%20of%20the%20alliance%20in%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20earlier%20this%20month.%20No%20mention%20of%20the%20killing%20was%2C%20however%2C%20made%20publicly%20before%20the%20summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20alliance%20have%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20allegations%20and%20some%20have%20urged%20India%20to%20cooperate%20with%20Canada%20in%20its%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20members%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%2C%20the%20US%20and%20Australia%2C%20are%20also%20part%20of%20the%20Quadrilateral%20Security%20Dialogue%2C%20or%20Quad%2C%20grouping%20with%20India%20and%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFounding%20And%20Objectives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20their%20intelligence%20cooperation%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20winning%20World%20War%20II%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20formalised%20the%20UKUSA%20agreement%20of%201946.%20The%20alliance%20expanded%20twice%20and%2C%20by%201956%2C%20Canada%2C%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20had%20also%20become%20its%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20charter%20from%20the%20alliance%20states%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20recognised%20that%20the%20intelligence%20agencies%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20countries%20cooperate%20operationally%20under%20formal%20or%20informal%20agreements%20and%20whereas%20each%20country%20has%20a%20variation%20of%20law%20on%20security%20of%20information%20or%20official%20secrets%20binding%20officials%20to%20secrecy%2C%20the%20Council%20Members%20commit%20to%20facilitating%20information%20sharing%20and%20collaboration%20between%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntelligence%20sharing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVarious%20agencies%20from%20all%20five%20countries%20share%20human%20intelligence%2C%20signal%20intelligence%2C%20security%20intelligence%2C%20geospatial%20intelligence%20and%20defence%20intelligence.%20Signals%20intelligence%2C%20or%20SIGINT%2C%20refers%20to%20information%20derived%20from%20electronic%20signals%20and%20networks%20such%20as%20communications%20systems%20-%20like%20the%20mobile%20network%20and%20the%20internet%20-%20radars%2C%20and%20weapons%20systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGeospatial%20intelligence%2C%20or%20location%20intelligence%2C%20deals%20with%20data%20such%20as%20satellite%20images%20and%20location%20information%20and%20%26quot%3B%20encompasses%20all%20aspects%20of%20imagery%20and%20geospatial%20information%20and%20services%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMember%20Statements%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%20on%20Monday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20had%20said%20his%20government%20had%20%26quot%3Bcredible%20allegations%26quot%3B%20linking%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20June%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bagents%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETerming%20the%20allegations%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20United%20States%20has%20said%20that%20it%20supports%20Canada's%20efforts%20to%20investigate%20the%20killing.%20It%20has%20also%20urged%20India%20to%20cooperate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertainly%20the%20President%20is%20mindful%20of%20these%20serious%20allegations%2C%20and%20they%20are%20very%20serious.%20And%20we%20support%20Canada's%20efforts%20to%20investigate%20this.%20We%20believe%20a%20fully%20transparent%20comprehensive%20investigation%20is%20the%20right%20approach%20so%20that%20we%20can%20all%20know%20exactly%20what%20happened%20and%20of%20course%2C%20we%20encourage%20India%20to%20cooperate%20with%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kirby%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAustralia%20has%20called%20the%20reports%20of%20the%20alleged%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20officials%20%26quot%3Bconcerning%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20has%20raised%20the%20issue%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20these%20are%20concerning%20reports%2C%20and%20I%20note%20that%20investigations%20are%20still%20underway%2C%20but%20obviously%20these%20are%20concerning%20reports%20and%20we%20are%20monitoring%20these%20developments%20closely%20with%20our%20partners%2C%20and%20we'll%20continue%20to%20do%20so...%20We%20have%20raised%20these%20issues%20with%20our%20Indian%20counterparts%2C%20as%20you%20would%20expect%20us%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Australian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Penny%20Wong%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%