2C%202018%2C%20has%20already%20spent%201%2C930%20days%20in%20jail.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20case%2C%20first%20handled%20by%20the%20Pune%20police%2C%20Raut%20was%20accused%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfunding%E2%80%9D%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20event%20organised%20on%20December%2031%2C%202017%20in%20Pune%E2%80%99s%20Shaniwarwada%20%E2%80%93%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20Brahmin%20hub%20%E2%80%93%20and%20which%20according%20to%20the%20state%20police%20had%20triggered%20violence%20a%20day%20later%20at%20Bhima%20Koregaon%2C%2030%20kilometres%20away%20from%20Pune.%20Taking%20over%20from%20the%20Pune%20police%2C%20the%20NIA%20had%20simply%20replicated%20the%20investigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20allegations%20against%20Raut%20were%20entirely%20based%20on%20letters%20allegedly%20procured%20from%20the%20laptop%20of%20his%20co-accused.%20In%20this%20letter%2C%20the%20agency%20claims%20a%20man%20named%20Mahesh%20had%20allegedly%20paid%20%E2%80%9C5L%E2%80%9D%20to%20organise%20the%20event.%20There%20is%20nothing%20more%20to%20substantiate%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20letter%20or%20that%20the%20said%20Mahesh%20mentioned%20in%20the%20letter%20is%20really%20Raut.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20Raut%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Mihir%20Desai%20had%20represented%20academic%20and%20civil%20liberties%20activist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbombay-hc-anand-teltumbde-bail%5C%22%3EAnand%20Teltumbde%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20case.%20Raut%E2%80%99s%20case%20too%20was%20largely%20argued%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20parity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDesai%2C%20representing%20Raut%2C%20had%20argued%20that%20his%20client%20was%20not%20a%20member%20of%20the%20banned%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20outfit%20as%20claimed%20by%20NIA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERaut%2C%20who%20completed%20his%20masters%20in%20social%20work%20from%20the%20coveted%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Sciences%20was%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Rural%20Development%20Fellowship.%20As%20a%20part%20of%20the%20fellowship%2C%20he%20began%20working%20in%20Gadchiroli%2C%20also%20his%20home%20town.%20On%20finishing%20the%20fellowship%20stint%2C%20Raut%20continued%20to%20work%20in%20the%20region%20and%20was%20vocal%20against%20the%20rampant%20mining%20and%20displacement%20of%20Adivasi%20communities%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NIA%20claims%20that%20his%20social%20work%20in%20the%20region%20was%20only%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccover%E2%80%9D%20for%20his%20Naxal%20activities%20in%20the%20conflict-prone%20areas%20of%20central%20India.%20The%20chargesheet%20claims%20that%20he%20operated%20under%20a%20fake%20name%2C%20%E2%80%9CRohit%20Verma%2C%E2%80%9D%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20last%20week%2C%20two%20of%20his%20co-accused%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felgar-parishad-bail-vernon-gonsalves-arun-ferreira-supreme-court%5C%22%3EVernon%20Gonsalves%20and%20Arun%20Ferreira%20were%20released%20on%20bail%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20NIA%20claimed%20that%20Raut%2C%20along%20with%20Ferreira%20had%20been%20involved%20in%20%E2%80%9Cinfluencing%20youths%E2%80%9D%20in%20places%20like%20TISS%20and%20Mumbai%20University%20to%20join%20the%20armed%20Naxal%20movement.%20These%20allegations%20are%20entirely%20based%20on%20statements%20of%20witnesses%20and%20there%20is%20no%20other%20direct%20evidence%20to%20substantiate%20these%20claims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERaut%20is%20one%20of%2016%20rights%20activists%2C%20scholars%20and%20lawyers%20arrested%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20case%20has%20been%20widely%20criticised%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20curb%20dissenting%20voices%2C%20instead%20of%20holding%20the%20real%20culprits%20of%20the%202018%20violence%20against%20Dalits%20in%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20responsible.%20Five%20of%20the%20accused%20%E2%80%93%20lawyer%20Sudha%20Bharadwaj%2C%20poet%20Varavara%20Rao%2C%20academic%20Teltumbe%2C%20lawyer%20Ferreira%20and%20activist%20Gonsalves%20%E2%80%93%20are%20currently%20out%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Father%20Stan%20Swamy%2C%20a%20tribal%20rights%20activist%20and%20Jesuit%20priest%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fremembering-stan-swamy-whose-struggle-was-driven-by-empathy-and-love%5C%22%3Epassed%20away%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20in%20custody.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695279863000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F10140122%2Fmahesh-raut_facebook.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmahesh-raut-activist-elgar-parishad-bombay-high-court-jail-nail%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2036-year-old%20tribal%20rights%20activist%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20five%20persons%20to%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20controversial%20case%2C%20on%20June%206%2C%202018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmahesh-raut-activist-elgar-parishad-bombay-high-court-jail-nail%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20pens%20a%20birthday%20post%20for%20Kareena%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695279733000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103830704%2Cimgsize-57936.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Falia-bhatt-pens-a-sweet-birthday-post-for-kareena-kapoor-khan-calls-her-the-ultimate-queen-see-photo%2Farticleshow%2F103830704.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103830704.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5