ollars-lean-workforces-ailing-san-francisco-2023-07-13%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEleven%2520of%2520the%2520country%2527s%2520top%2Cfrom%2520venture%2520capital%2520firm%2520NFX.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E11%20of%20the%20top%2020%20AI%20companies%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20data%20from%20VC%20firm%20NFX%2C%20which%20was%20shared%20with%20Insider%2C%20showed.%20Many%20of%20these%20companies%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fartificial-intelligence-companies-are-flocking-to-san-francisco-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehunting%20for%20office%20space%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFintech%20startup%20Brex%20decided%20to%20close%20its%20San%20Francisco%20office%20and%20switch%20to%20remote%20working%20during%20the%20pandemic%20but%20reopened%20a%20San%20Francisco%20location%20earlier%20this%20year%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20the%20opportunities%20offered%20by%20the%20AI%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22San%20Francisco.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F643f00aaae06160018a2dfc8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESan%20Francisco%20skyline.%3Cp%3EAlexander%20Spatari%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20cofounder%20and%20co-CEO%2C%20Henrique%20Dubugras%2C%20was%20really%20excited%20by%20what%20he%20saw%20as%20going%20on%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20with%20regards%20to%20AI%20and%20how%20big%20of%20an%20opportunity%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Tannenbaum%2C%20Brex's%20COO%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20wanted%20to%20get%20closer%20to%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20sheer%20density%20of%20talent%20and%20innovation%20in%20San%20Francisco%20meant%20the%20city%20remained%20an%20ideal%20place%20for%20startups%20to%20develop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20forward-thinking%20town%2C%26quot%3B