mit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20being%20offered%20a%20presidential%20suite%2C%20his%20delegation%20refused%20to%20stay%20there%20and%20instead%20stayed%20at%20a%20regular%20room%20in%20the%20same%20hotel%2C%20sources%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEvery%20global%20leader%20who%20had%20come%20to%20India%20for%20the%20G20%20was%20provided%20VVIP%20hotels%20with%20the%20presidential%20suite%2C%20with%20complete%20security%20protocols.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20delegation%20told%20Indian%20security%20agencies%20that%20this%20decision%20is%20being%20taken%20due%20to%20cost%20considerations.%20However%2C%20the%20Indian%20agencies%20have%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20information%20about%20the%20exact%20reason%20behind%20Trudeau's%20staying%20in%20a%20normal%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20this%20was%20not%20the%20only%20irregular%20episode%20from%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20visit%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20PM%20was%20scheduled%20to%20depart%20from%20India%20on%20September%2010%2C%20however%2C%20he%20had%20to%20extend%20his%20stay%20after%20a%20technical%20snag%20on%20his%20Airbus%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20that%20the%20Indian%20side%20had%20offered%20services%20of%20aircraft%20'Air%20India%20One'%20to%20Canadian%20PM%20Trudeau%20and%20his%20delegation%20to%20fly%20back%2C%20after%20coming%20to%20know%20about%20the%20delay%20in%20the%20departure%20of%20the%20Canadian%20PM%20and%20accompanying%20delegation%20due%20to%20the%20glitch%20in%20their%20special%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Canadian%20side%20declined%20the%20offer%20and%20instead%20chose%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20backup%20aircraft%2C%20sources%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%20Finally%2C%20Trudeau%20was%20able%20to%20depart%20from%20India%20only%20on%20September%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20tensions%20between%20India%20and