%20after%20the%20injury%2C%20coming%20back%20in%20January%20and%20trying%20to%20find%20that%20rhythm%20again...it's%20been%20OK%2C%20but%20there%20have%20been%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%26quot%3B%20Sindhu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20former%20India%20coach%20Vimal%20Kumar%20had%20said%20that%20repeated%20failures%20in%20tournaments%20this%20season%20has%20dented%20Sindhu's%20confidence%20and%20not%20much%20should%20be%20expected%20from%20the%20ace%20Indian%20shuttler%20at%20the%20Asian%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695277800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fjrl5em3o_pv-sindhu-virat-kohli-afp_625x300_21_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Fvirat-kohli-went-through-pv-sindhu-struggling-for-form-ahead-of-asian-games-talks-about-comeback-4409606%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22PV%20Sindhu%2C%20who%20is%20struggling%20for%20form%20ahead%20of%20the%20Asian%20Games%2C%20has%20revealed%20how%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20star%20Virat%20Kohli%20inspired%20her%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Fvirat-kohli-went-through-pv-sindhu-struggling-for-form-ahead-of-asian-games-talks-about-comeback-4409606%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Fvirat-kohli-went-through-pv-sindhu-struggling-for-form-ahead-of-asian-games-talks-about-comeback-4409606%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Fvirat-kohli-went-through-pv-sindhu-struggling-for-form-ahead-of-asian-games-talks-about-comeback-4409606%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22YouTuber%20Hosts%20Fake%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20For%20Viewership%20Record%2C%20Internet%20Divided%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmerican%20streamer%20and%20co-owner%20of%20Kick%20Adin%20Ross%20earlier%20claimed%20that%20he%20would%20be%20getti