%2Fyoutuber-adin-ross-hosts-fake-kim-jong-un-for-viewership-record-internet-divided-4409650%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fyoutuber-adin-ross-hosts-fake-kim-jong-un-for-viewership-record-internet-divided-4409650%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20Says%20Behind%20Killing%20Of%20Khalistani%20Terrorist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJailed%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20today%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkhalistani-terrorist-sukha-duneke-killed-in-canada-in-inter-gang-rivalry-say-sources-4409330%5C%22%3ESukhdool%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Canada.%20Sukhdool%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Sukha%20Duneke%2C%20was%20killed%20last%20night%20in%20Canada%20in%20inter-gang%20violence.%20Duneke%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Khalistan%20movement%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuneke%20was%20a%20%26quot%3BCategory%20A%26quot%3B%20gangster%20from%20Punjab's%20Moga.%20He%20fled%20to%20Canada%20on%20a%20fake%20passport%20in%202017%20and%20was%20a%20close%20associate%20of%20gangster%20and%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Arshdeep%20Dalla.%20He%20was%20one%20of%2043%20gangsters%20with%20links%20to%20Khalistan%20and%20Canada%20mentioned%20in%20a%20list%20released%20by%20the%20anti-terror%20agency%20NIA%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20Bishnoi's%20gang%20claimed%20that%20Duneke%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20murders%20of%20gangsters%20Gurlal%20Brar%20and%20Vicky%20Middukhera.%20The%20gang%20termed%20Duneke%20a%20%26quot%3Bdrug%20addict'%20who%20got%20%26quot%3Bpunished%20for%20his%20sins%26quot%3B%20and%20warned%20that%20their%20enemies%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20survive%20in%20India%20or%20any%20other%20country%20for%20that%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and