hiba-troubled-electronics-and-energy-giant-to-leave-stock-market-after-more-than-70-years-12966032%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canada%20Rejects%20India's%20Travel%20Advisory%20Amid%20Escalating%20Diplomatic%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20government%20has%20rejected%20a%20travel%20advisory%20issued%20by%20India%20about%20security%20risks%20in%20Canada%2C%20claiming%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20safest%20countries%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20called%20for%20calm%20amid%20the%20escalating%20diplomatic%20row%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20in%20this%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20of%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26quot%3B%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20government%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20June%20unleashed%20a%20diplomatic%20row%20with%20India%20rejecting%20the%20charges%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%26quot%3B%20and%20kicking%20out%20a%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat%20in%20a%20tit-for-tat%20move%20to%20Ottawa's%20expulsion%20of%20an%20Indian%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20on%20Wednesday%20advised%20all%20its%20citizens%20living%20in%20Canada%20and%20those%20contemplating%20travelling%20there%20to%20exercise%20%26quot%3Butmost%20caution%26quot%3B%20in%20view%20of%20growing%20anti-India%20activities%20and%20%26quot%3Bpolitically-condoned%26quot%3B%20hate%20crimes%20in%20the%20North%20American%20country%2C%20as%20the%20diplomatic%20row%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20threatened%20to%20snowball%20into%20a%20major%20confrontation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20strongly-worded%20advisory%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20in%20New%20Delhi%20referred%20to%20%26quot%3Bthreats%26quot%3B%20targeting%20Indian%20diplomats%20and%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%20that%20oppose%20the%20%26quot%3Banti-India%20agenda%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20asked%20Indian%20nationals%20to%20avoid%20travelling%20to%20regions%20and%20potential%20venues%20in%20Canada%20which%20have%20seen%20such%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanada's%20Immigration%20Minister%20Marc%20Miller%20sought%20to%20reassure%20Indian%20nationals%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20it%20is%20safe%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20country%20even%20as%20a%20terrorist%20of%20the%20Sikh%20separatist%20movement%20banned%20in%20India%20has%20announced%20plans%20for%20rallies%20in%20Canadian%20cities%20on%20Monday%20that%20seek%20the%20closing%20of%20New%20Delhi's%20diplomatic%20missions%20in%20the%20country%2C%20The%20Globe%20and%20Mail%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I%20think%20everyone%20knows%20Canada%20is%20a%20safe%20country%20and%20given%20the%20events%20of%20the%20last%20two%20or%20three%20days%20and%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20allegations%20that%20-%20it's%20important%20for%20everyone%20to%20stay%20calm%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20Canadian%20Press%20quoted%20Miller%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCanada%20by%20any%20standard%20is%20one%20of%20the%20safest%20if%20not%20the%20safest%20countries%20in%20the%20world%20that%20is%20governed%20by%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20people%20should%20read%20that%20statement%20for%20what%20it%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Miller%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20acknowledged%20that%20Canadian%20allegations%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26quot%3B%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20government%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20have%20heightened%20tensions%20with%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20what%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20said%20quite%20clearly%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20(Narendra)%20Modi%2C%20the%20allegations%20are%20very%20serious%2C%20and%20these%20are%20discussions%20that%20have%20to%20continue%20with%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20emotions%20are%20running%20high%2C%20and%20we've%20asked%20everyone%20just%20to%20stay%20calm%20given%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20allegations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMinister%20of%20Housing%2C%20Infrastructure%20and%20Communities%20Sean%20Fraser%20said%20that%20he%20would%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20specifics%20of%20the%20probe%20into%20Nijjar's%20death%20because%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20compromise%20any%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Canadians%20should%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20security%20services'%20ability%20to%20investigate%20the%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20that%20if%20we%20believe%20in%20justice%2C%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20process%20that%20gets%20us%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Canadian%20Broadcasting%20Corporation%20quoted%20Mr%20Fraser%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20sure%20there%20are%20good%20reasons%20not%20to%20share%20details%20that%20may%20ground%20such%20extraordinary%20allegations%20because%20protecting%20the%20process%20of%20getting%20to%20a%20just%20result%20is%20extremely%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Fraser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20a%20country%20that%20was%20built%20on%20migration.%20If%20you're%20not%20from%20an%20indigenous%20community%2C%20you%20came%20from%20somewhere%20else%2C%20and%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20right%20now%20the%20people%20I'm%20talking%20to%20here%2C%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20see%20divisions%20based%20on%20whether%20you%20are%20Sikh%2C%20Hindu%20or%20Muslim.%20They%20want%20to%20come%20together%20as%20Canadians%20and%20promote%20peaceful%20dialogue%2C%20even%20in%20the%20most%20difficult%20conversations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20obviously%20a%20tragedy%20that%20played%20out.%20The%20allegations%20are%20extremely%20serious.%20And%20we're%20going%20to%20treat%20them%20seriously.%20We're%20always%20concerned%20about%20the%20safety%