Thursday%20morning%2C%20the%20Punjab%20Police%20has%20begun%20rounding%20up%20many%20associates%20of%20Brar%20and%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20and%20other%20people%20who%20have%20dealings%20with%20them.%20Police%20officials%20said%20that%20it%20has%20often%20been%20seen%20that%20aides%20of%20Brar%20and%20Bishnoi%2C%20even%20when%20they%20are%20behind%20bars%2C%20entice%20young%20people%20accused%20of%20petty%20offences%20like%20drug%20peddling%20and%20try%20and%20push%20them%20into%20committing%20bigger%20crimes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20said%20the%20gang's%20members%20and%20associates%20give%20these%20young%20people%20an%20ideological%20push%20and%20lure%20them%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20money%20to%20get%20them%20to%20carry%20out%20murders%20and%20targeted%20killings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20is%20being%20undertaken%20in%20all%2022%20districts%20of%20the%20state%20and%20a%20detailed%20report%20on%20the%20detainees%20and%20the%20evidence%20gathered%20will%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20police%20brass%20after%20it%20is%20completed.%20The%20crackdown%20is%20also%20aimed%20at%20cutting%20off%20the%20supply%20chain%20of%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorked%20As%20Trucker%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGoldy%20Brar%2C%20alias%20Satinderjit%20Singh%2C%20is%20a%20native%20of%20Muktsar%20district%20in%20Punjab%20and%20became%20friends%20with%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20when%20they%20were%20both%20active%20in%20student%20politics%20in%20Chandigarh%20around%20ten%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBrar%20moved%20to%20Canada%20on%20a%20student%20visa%20five%20years%20ago%20and%20worked%20as%20a%20trucker%20for%20a%20while.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20country%20had%20named%20him%20on%20its%20list%20of%2025%20most-wanted%20fugitives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESinger%20Sidhu%20Moosewala%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20his%20SUV%20near%20his%20village%2C%20Moosa%2C%20in%20Punjab's%20Mansa%20district%20on%20June%2029.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20Brar%20had%20said%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20that%20he%20had%20planned%20the%20murder%20to%20avenge%20the%20killing%20of%20another%20gangster.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiplomatic%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%20on%20Monday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20had%20said%20his%20government%20had%20%26quot%3Bcredible%20allegations%26quot%3B%20linking%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20June%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bagents%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20has%20rejected%20the%20allegation%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%20and%20motivated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanada%20and%20India%20have%20both%20expelled%20a%20diplomat%20from%20the%20other%20country%20since%20the%20stand-off%20began.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20India%20also%20issued%20a%20travel%20advisory%20for%20Canada%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20latter%20updated%20its%20own%20travel%20advisory%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%20was%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20banned%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20and%20was%20killed%20in%20Surrey%20in%20the%20Canadian%20province%20of%20British%20Columbia%20on%20June%2018.%20Reports%20emerged%20on%20Thursday%20of%20another%20terrorist%2C%20Sukhdool%20Singh%2C%20being%20killed%20in%20inter-gang%20violence%20in%20Canada.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695274560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2F19c2h1lg_goldy-brar-gangster_650x400_30_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpunjab-police-launches-statewide-crackdown-on-aides-of-gangster-goldy-brar-4409301%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20India's%20diplomatic%20stand-off%20with%20Canada%2C%20the%20Punjab%20Police%20has%20launched%20a%20statewide%20crackdown%20on%20the%20accomplices%20of%20gangster%20Goldy%20Brar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%