rma%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20team%20achieves%20what%20MS%20Dhoni's%20side%20did%20in%20the%202011%20edition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMS%20Dhoni%2C%20however%2C%20was%20seen%20in%20a%20different%20avatar%20as%20he%20could%20be%20seen%20joining%20a%20procession%20celebrating%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%202023.%20The%20video%20has%20been%20widely%20shared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%20celebrating%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Video%20of%20the%20day....!!!!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FuWZyAsdsCP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FuWZyAsdsCP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Mufaddal%20Vohra%20(%40mufaddal_vohra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmufaddal_vohra%2Fstatus%2F1704718110182490457%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20this%20time%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Co.%20are%20carrying%20the%20hopes%20of%20the%20country.%20India%20have%20not%20won%20any%20ICC%20event%20since%202013%20and%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%20is%20a%20brilliant%20opportunity%20to%20end%20that%20drought.%20Playing%20at%20home%20brings%20with%20it%20great%20pressure.%20Former%20Australia%20wicketkeeper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Adam%20Gilchrist%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F201-adam-gilchrist-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAdam%20Gilchrist%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20himself%20a%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20winner%2C%20had%20a%20piece%20of%20special%20advice%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20by%20Sportstar%2C%20which%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20will%20your%20advice%20be%20for%20the%20youngsters%20like%20Gill%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-