itored-probe-into-pulwama-terror-attack%2Fcid%2F1967699%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20on%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20speech%20at%20an%20event%20at%20the%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20in%20which%20he%20spoke%20of%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20government%20on%20the%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMalik%20was%20the%20last%20governor%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20was%20in%20position%20when%20the%20attack%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20demand%20Supreme%20Court-monitored%20investigations%20into%20the%20Pulwama%20terror%20attack%20in%20which%20our%2040%20troops%20were%20martyred.%20So%20far%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%20have%20maintained%20a%20deafening%20silence%20on%20the%20tragedy%20and%20have%20failed%20to%20own%20up%20to%20the%20glaring%20lapses%20that%20led%20to%20the%20killings%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20Malik%20as%20having%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Malik%20has%20spoken%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20accountability%20in%20this%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsatya-pal-malik-full-interview-pulwama-modi%5C%22%3Eexplosive%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Malik%20had%20said%20that%20the%20CRPF%20had%20asked%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20for%20aircraft%20to%20ferry%20their%20people%20%E2%80%9Cbecause%20such%20a%20big%20convoy%20never%20goes%20by%20road.%E2%80%9D%20The%20home%20ministry%20refused%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20told%20it%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20the%20evening%20that%20this%20has%20happened%20due%20to%20our%20fault.%20Had%20we%20given%20the%20aircraft%2C%20this%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20happened.%20To%20which%20he%20told%20me%20that%20I%20should%20keep%20quiet%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20had%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20NSO%20Ajit%20Doval%20had%20also%20said%20this%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMalik%20also%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceight%20to%2010%20link%20roads%20were%20unmanned%E2%80%9D%2C%20pointing%20to%20an%20overall%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Pulwama%20attack%20had%20taken%20place%20just%20months%20before%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20In%20retaliation%2C%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20carried%20out%20airstrikes%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Balakot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Malik%20disagreed%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%20on%20the%20phrasing%20that%20Modi%20used%20the%20attack%20to%20leverage%20his%20re-election%20pitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20language%2C%20I%20can%20just%20say%20that%20instead%20of%20going%20to%20the%20root%20cause%20or%20the%20starting%20point%20of%20that%20matter%2C%20or%20maybe%20if%20we%20also%20went%20to%20the%20start%20and%20completely%20investigated%20every%20thing%2C%20we%20might%20have%20to%20change%20things%20for%20our%20own%20personal%20benefit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20he%20struck%20a%20clearer%20tone%20and%20appeared%20to%20blame%20Modi%20for%20politicising%20the%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CModi%20had%20politicised%20the%20killings%20of%2040%20CRPF%20soldiers%20and%20the%20IAF%20strikes%20in%20Balakot%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20had%20even%20asked%20first-time%20voters%20to%20dedicate%20their%20vote%20to%20the%20valiant%20soldiers%20who%20carried%20out%20the%20air%20strike%20in%20Balakot%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20over%20four%20years%20since%20then%2C%20but%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20fix%20accountability.%20Winning%20elections%20is%20his%20only%20priority.%20The%20people%20of%20this%20country%20need%20to%20remain%20alert%20that%20similar%20attacks%20can%20happen%20this%20time%20too%20before%20the%20parliamentary%20polls%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20added.%3C%2Fp%3