they%20are%20deeply%20connected%20to%20the%20Hindu-Canadian%20community.%20Canadian%20Hindus%20and%20Sikhs%20are%20connected%20through%20family%20relationships%20and%20shared%20social%20and%20cultural%20ties%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArya%20stated%20that%20this%20%26quot%3Bdirect%20attack%26quot%3B%20on%20Hindu%20Canadians%20by%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Canadian%20Khalistan%20movement%20is%20the%20further%20escalation%20of%20the%20recent%20attacks%20on%20Hindu%20temples%20and%20public%20celebration%20of%20the%20assassination%20of%20Hindu%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20by%20%26quot%3Bterrorists%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCanada%20has%20high%20moral%20values%20and%20we%20fully%20uphold%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20expressed%20dismay%20at%20%26quot%3Bglorification%20of%20terrorism%26quot%3B%20and%20hate%20crime%20being%20allowed%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%26quot%3Bfreedom%20of%20expression%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20understand%20how%20the%20glorification%20of%20terrorism%20or%20a%20hate%20crime%20targeting%20a%20religious%20group%20is%20allowed%20in%20the%20name%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%20There%20would%20be%20an%20outrage%20in%20Canada%20if%20a%20white%20supremacist%20attacked%20any%20group%20of%20racialized%20Canadians%20asking%20them%20to%20get%20out%20of%20our%20country.%20But%20apparently%2C%20this%20Khalistani%20leader%20can%20get%20away%20with%20this%20hate%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArya%20added%20that%20the%20Hindu%20Canadians%20keep%20a%20low%20profile%2C%20are%20considered%20soft%20targets%2C%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Banti-Hindu%20elements%26quot%3B%20cannot%20digest%20the%20success%20of%20Hindu-Canadians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20well-organized%20groups%20claiming%20to%20represent%20their%20faiths%20have%20been%20attacking%20Hindu-Canadian%20community%20leaders%2C%20Hindu