%2520(0.2%2525).%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20last%202011%20census%20in%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Sikhs%20were%20just%201.7%25%20and%20their%20population%20declined%20from%20the%20last%20census%20in%202001%20by%200.2%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0looks%20at%20the%20factors%20behind%20the%20Khalistan%20narrative%20and%20how%20it%20has%20failed%20to%20find%20any%20traction%20in%20Punjab%20over%20the%20years.%20Even%20the%20recent%20protests%20led%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famritpal-singh-radical-sikh-politics-rise%5C%22%3Eself-styled%20pro-Khalistan%20leader%20of%20%E2%80%98Waris%20Punjab%20De%E2%80%99%2C%20Amritpal%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20petered%20out%20within%20a%20matter%20of%20days.%20Amritpal%20along%20with%20his%20supporters%20was%20arrested%20in%20April%20this%20year%20and%20is%20currently%20lodged%20in%20Dibrugarh%20jail%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETalking%20to%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Chandigarh%20based%20senior%20journalist%20Jagtar%20Singh%20who%20has%20written%20two%20books%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKhalistan%20Struggle%3A%20A%20Non-Movement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERivers%20on%20Fire%3A%20Khalistan%20Struggle%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ediscussed%20the%20India-Canada%20diplomatic%20row%20in%20the%20global%20perspective.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-trudeau-india-murder-us-uk-australia%5C%22%3Einformation%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20interference%20in%20Canada%20has%20been%20shared%20by%20The%20Five%20Eyes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20intelligence%20alliance%20of%20Australia%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK%20and%20not%20just%20by%20Canada.%20When%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20left%20India%20without%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20he%20immediately%20landed%20in%20Vietnam%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fus-president-biden-says-he-raised-importance-of-human-rights-and-free-press-with-pm-modi%5C%22%3Esharply%20attacked%20PM%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Everything%20is%20linked.%20The%20western%20world%20is%20closing%20up%20against%20Modi%20for%20certain%20reasons%20but%20when%20a%20PM%20says%20something%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20house%2C%20he%20is%20supposed%20to%20have%20some%20credible%20information%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20which%20they%20have%20reacted%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20306px)%2085vw%2C%20306px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12225153%2F2020_6largeimg_1134232441.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22306%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12225153%2F2020_6largeimg_1134232441.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12225153%2F2020_6largeimg_1134232441-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12225153%2F2020_6largeimg_1134232441-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-509559%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22306%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGurpatwant%20Pannu.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%2FFile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20on%20the%20Khalistan%20narrative%20abroad%2C%20the%20author%20rather%20posed%20a%20question%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20over%20its%20failure%20to%20act%20against%20US%20based%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%20leader%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannu.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CKhalistanis%20have%20been%20active%20in%20Canada%20over%20the%20years.%20Even%20before%20Operation%20Bluestar%2C%20they%20were%20active%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Canada%20and%20the%20US.%20But%20what%20is%20intriguing%20is%20that%20the%20face%20of%20Khalistan%20movement%20outside%20India%20is%20Pannu.%20How%20come%20we%20(India)%20are%20not%20seeking%20his%20extradition%3F%20India%20is%20blaming%20Canada%20but%20Pannu%20is%20based%20in%20the%20US.%20Even%20though%20several%20cases%20were%20filed%20against%20him%2C%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20him.%20India%20needs%20to%20explain%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EContrary%20to%20this%2C%20Jagtar%20said%20that%20India%20had%20announced%20a%20prize%20on%20the%20head%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20but%20he%20was%20a%20public%20figure%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20some%20contradictions.%20We%20have%20been%20claiming%20that%20the%20Khalistan%20issue%20has%20phased%20out%20but%20it%20has%20come%20to%20the%20centre%20stage%20again.%20India%20has%20always%20approached%20this%20issue%20as%20a%20law-and-order%20problem%20but%20if%20it%20was%20so%20then%20why%20does%20this%20sentiment%20continue%20to%20prevail%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20questioned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKhalistan%20not%20an%20issue%20in%20Punjab%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20Khalistan%20issue%20not%20finding%20any%20traction%20in%20Punjab%20over%20years%2C%20the%20senior%20journalist%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CKhalistan%20was%20never%20an%20issue%20in%20the%20democratic%20domain.%20Even%20the%20SAD%20used%20to%20oppose%20the%20Khalistanis%20but%20the%20movement%20was%20there.%20The%20Indian%20government%20should%20take%20it%20as%20a%20political%20challenge.%20The%20Khalistan%20struggle%20needs%20closure%20because%20that%20sense%20of%20alienation%20among%20the%20Sikhs%20is%20continuing.%20Almost%20every%20third%20family%20in%20Punjab%20was%20settled%20in%20Canada%20now%20or%20for%20that%20matter%20other%20countries%20abroad.%20Why%20is%20India%20silent%20on%20such%20a%20sensitive%20matter%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EListing%20major%20reasons%2C%20he%20said%20it%20was%20the%20fear%20of%20the%20level%20of%20state%20oppression%2C%20UAPA%20and%20NSA%20cases%2C%20which%20stops%20people%20from%20even%20talking%20about%20Khalistan.%20%E2%80%9CHere%20people%20are%20put%20behind%20bars%20whereas%20in%20the%20west%2C%20they%20allow%20open%20discussion.%20People%20do%20not%20even%20talk%20about%20it.%20Let%20us%20not%20forget%20that%20Sikhs%20are%20the%20only%20people%20who%20ruled%20this%20region%20at%20one%20point%20of%20time.%20That%20sentiment%20of%20being%20the%20rulers%20always%20remains.%20Having%20sentiments%20is%20one%20thing%20and%20demanding%20a%20separate%20state%20is%20an%20altogether%20different%20subject.%20In%20the%20West%2C%20we%20have%20the%20example%20of%20Scotland%20and%20Quebec%2C%20where%20referendums%20have%20been%20held%20but%20that%20was%20not%20the%20case%20in%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20senior%20journalist%20also%20shared%20how%20he%20tried%20to%20get%20information%20through%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%20(RTI)%20from%20Punjab%2C%20central%20government%20and%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20when%20he%20was%20writing%20his%20second%20book.%20%E2%80%9CI%20even%20failed%20to%20get%20the%20copy%20of%20the%20file%20on%20who%20requisitioned%20the%20Army%20but%20the%20government%20never%20shared.%20The%20government%20should%20come%20out%20with%20the%20entire%20information%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENotably%2C%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20Punjab%20Assembly%20Elections%20in%202022%2C%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janta%20Party%20(BJP)%20while%20releasing%20its%20election%20manifesto%20announced%20the%20constitution%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98Truth%20and%20Reconciliation%20Commission%E2%80%99%2C%20to%20address%20the%20grievances%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20who%20were%20seeking%20justice%20and%20announced%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20each.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20then%20SAD%20president%20Parkash%20Singh%20Badal%20had%20also%20announced%20a%20similar%20commission%20in%20their%20election%20manifesto%20in%201997%2C%20which%20ended%20up%20as%20a%20mere%20lip%20service%20while%20the%20simmering%20discontent%20within%20the%20community%20kept%20growing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F27183039%2FScreen-Shot-2020-09-27-at-6.30.12-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22995%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F27183039%2FScreen-Shot-2020-09-27-at-6.30.12-PM.png%20995w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F27183039%2FScreen-Shot-2020-09-27-at-6.30.12-PM-300x194.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-482068%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22644%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIn%20this%20file%20photo%2C%20dated%20April%2026%2C%202019%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20seen%20with%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20leader%20Parkash%20Singh%20Badal%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Bihar%20CM%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20Varanasi.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%2FFile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFormer%20Sociologist%20calls%20Khalistan%20a%20non-issue%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20Head%20of%20Department%20of%20Sociology%20from%20Panjab%20University%2C%20Chandigarh%20Professor%20Manjit%20Singh%20categorically%20ruled%20out%20any%20pro-Khalistan%20sentiment%20in%20Punjab.%20%E2%80%9CKhalistan%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20in%20Punjab.%20It%20was%20never%20a%20public%20issue%20at%20all.%20But%2C%20yes%20with%20the%20recent%20standoff%20between%20India-Canada%2C%20it%20has%20become%20a%20global%20and%20political%20issue.%20The%20fact%20is%20that%20there%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20what%20the%20East%20and%20West%20practices%20in%20terms%20of%20its%20laws%20and%20rights.%20Whether%20it%20was%20Amritpal%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20issue%2C%20the%20killing%20of%20Paramjit%20Singh%20Panjwar%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Avtar%20Singh%20Khanda%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20or%20diplomatic%20tension%20with%20UK%20or%20Canada%2C%20there%20are%20no%20takers%20for%20Khalistan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sociologist%20emphasised%20that%20Punjab%20has%20always%20remained%20a%20peaceful%20state%20but%20Punjabis%20stakes%20were%20high%20in%20Canada.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20onus%20is%20on%20the%20Canadian%20government%20now%20to%20provide%20evidence.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Indian%20government%20should%20handle%20this%20issue%20sensibly%20and%20delicately%2C%20as%20lakhs%20of%20students%2C%20working%20class%20and%20the%20elderly%20were%20residing%20in%20Canada%20through%20one%20or%20the%20other%20immigration%20program%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20a%20section%20of%20people%20feel%20strongly%20for%20Khalistan%2C%20they%20can%20do%20it%20either%20in%20Canada%20or%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESGPC%20on%20India-Canada%20standoff%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Shiromani%20Gurdwara%20Parbhandak%20Committee%20(SGPC)%20president%20Harjinder%20Singh%20Dhami%20also%20issued%20a%20statement%20stating%20that%20the%20governments%20of%20India%20and%20Canada%20should%20adopt%20an%20agenda%20of%20serious%20consideration%20instead%20of%20accusations.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20Canada%20based%20Sikh%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20the%20expelling%20of%20a%20diplomatic%20officer%20of%20India%20by%20the%20Canadian%20government%20after%20allegations%20were%20levelled%20against%20him%20raises%20many%20questions%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSikhs%20have%20always%20kept%20their%20presence%20and%20existence%20high%20in%20the%20country%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20whole%20world%20with%20their%20hardworking%20nature%20and%20intellectual%20strength%2C%20but%20despite%20this%2C%20Sikhs%20always%20have%20to%20struggle%20for%20their%20rights.%20It%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20government%20of%20the%20country%20to%20adopt%20a%20sincere%20approach%20regarding%20such%20matters%20related%20to%20the%20Sikhs%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20and%20not%20to%20allow%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20distrust%20among%20the%20community%20members%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESikh%20radical%20outfit%20Dal%20Khalsa%20questioned%20silence%20of%20Indian%20government%20over%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannu%E2%80%99s%20role%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20Khalistan%2C%20Kanwarpal%20Singh%20from%20Dal%20Khalsa%2C%20a%20Sikh%20radical%20group%2C%20told%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0that%20this%20was%20likely%20to%20happen.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20last%20six%20to%20seven%20years%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20was%20after%20the%20Trudeau%20government%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20Khalistan.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20India%20Today%2C%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20magazines%20of%20India%20carried%20a%20cover%20page%20story%20on%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20as%20a%20Khalistan%20supporter%20some%20years%20ago.%20The%20India-Canada%20row%20over%20Khalistan%20narrative%20was%20bound%20to%20reach%20climax%20sooner%20or%20later.%20For%20once%20at%20least%20Justin%20Trudeau%20brought%20the%20issue%20of%20extrajudicial%20killings%20on%20a%20global%20platform.%20We%20have%20been%20raising%20our%20voices%20against%20this%20for%20a%20long%20time%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Dal%20Khalsa%20leader%20also%20brought%20up%20the%20question%20of%20why%20the%20Indian%20government%20was%20not%20taking%20any%20action%20against%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannu%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20banned%20outfit%20%E2%80%98Sikhs%20for%20Justice%E2%80%99%20(SFJ).%20%E2%80%9CGurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannu%20is%20a%20US%20citizen%20and%20facing%20over%2018%20FIRs.%20Have%20they%20taken%20any%20action%20against%20Pannu%3F%20If%20not%2C%20then%20why%3F%20He%20is%20allowed%20to%20run%20his%20actions%20but%20Sikhs%20in%20Canada%20were%20being%20targeted.%20Let%20us%20not%20forget%20that%20Trudeau%20has%20indicted%20a%20government%20while%20speaking%20in%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20when%20asked%20that%20there%20were%20no%20takers%20for%20Khalistan%20narrative%20in%20Punjab%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20west%2C%20Kanwarpal%20Singh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20afraid%20of%20the%20Indian%20government.%20They%20enjoy%20freedom%20of%20expression%20in%20the%20west.%20In%20fact%2C%20whatever%20is%20happening%20in%20terms%20of%20Khalistan%20ideology%20on%20the%20foreign%20land%20was%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20incidents%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20Punjab.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2FOperation-Blue-Star_PTI.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sikh%20youth%20flash%20swords%20and%20raise%20slogans%20about%20Khalistan%20while%20taking%20a%20round%20of%20the%20Golden%20Temple%20in%20Amritsar%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20anniversary%20of%20Operation%20Bluestar%20in%202015.%20Credit%3A%20PTI%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-194720%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22571%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESikh%20youth%20flash%20swords%20and%20raise%20slogans%20about%20Khalistan%20while%20taking%20a%20round%20of%20the%20Golden%20Temple%20in%20Amritsar%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20anniversary%20of%20Operation%20Bluestar%20in%202015.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%2FFile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFarm%20protests%2C%20not%20Khalistan%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20farmers%20protesting%20against%20the%20three%20farm%20bills%2C%20suddenly%20brought%20in%20without%20consultation%20in%20September%202020%2C%20or%20a%20proper%20vote%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20led%20to%20widespread%20protests%20on%20the%20streets.%20The%20protests%20finally%20forced%20Modi%20himself%20to%20announce%20their%20withdrawl.%20But%20before%20caving%2C%20the%20union%20government%20and%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20supporters%20on%20social%20media%2C%20went%20all%20the%20way%20to%20suggest%20and%20explicitly%20tar%20the%20protests%20with%20being%20inspired%20by%20Khalistan.%20Comments%20by%20popstar%20Rihanna%2C%20protesting%20widespread%20internet%20shutdowns%20that%20followed%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20farm%20protests%20were%20also%20given%20given%20a%20Khalistani%20and%20anti-national%20twist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-despite-rightwing-propaganda-khalistani-angle-finds-little-traction%5C%22%3EFarmers%E2%80%99%20Protest%3A%20Despite%20Rightwing%20Propaganda%2C%20%E2%80%98Khalistani%E2%80%99%20Angle%20Finds%20Little%20Traction%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edespite%20concerted%20efforts%20to%20defame%20farmers%20protesting%20against%20the%20three%20agriculture%20laws%20by%20labelling%20them%20%E2%80%98Khalistanis%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20this%20got%20no%20traction%20among%20the%20general%20public.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20more%20people%20came%20out%20in%20support%20of%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20put%20the%20three%20fa