2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eric%20McAskill%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20together%20with%20their%20two%20children.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65000e554717fd0019fc7dab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEric%20McAskill%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20together%20with%20their%20two%20children.%3Cp%3EEric%20McAskill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EMcAskill's%20love%20affair%20with%20Japan%20started%20when%20he%20was%20a%20kid.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Vancouver%2C%20Canada%2C%20he%20grew%20up%20surrounded%20by%20many%20Japanese%20friends%20who%20often%20invited%20him%20to%20their%20houses%2C%20providing%20him%20with%20insights%20into%20their%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20grew%20up%20going%20for%20family%20dinners%2C%20sitting%20around%20the%20table%20with%20all%20the%20grandparents%2C%20and%20I%20came%20to%20really%20love%20the%20culture%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20McAskill%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20he%20would%20find%20himself%20visiting%20Japan%20again%20and%20again%2C%20each%20time%20visiting%20a%20different%20prefecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20from%20Abashiri%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20northern%20points%20in%20Hokkaido%2C%20all%20the%20way%20down%20through%20Japan%20to%20the%20island%20of%20Yonaguni%2C%20which%20is%20right%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Taiwan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McAskill%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20his%20akiya.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6507b544f05aa00019bddf99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcAskill%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20his%20akiya.%3Cp%3EEric%20McAskill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMcAskill%20had%20no%20problems%20buying%20property%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20parts%20of%20Japan%20is%20that%20there%20are%20no%20restrictions%20or%20limitations%20on%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.japan-property.jp%2Fguide-to-buying-properties1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20foreigners%20owning%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20McAskill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcAskill%20bought%20his%20akiya%20through%20an%20akiya%20bank%2C%20which%20is%20a%20database%20maintained%20by%20the%20local%20municipalities%20for%20abandoned%20or%20vacant%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20person%20to%20bid%20starts%20to%20enter%20into%20negotiations%20with%20the%20owner%2C%26quot%3B%20McAskill%20said%20of%20the%20bidding%20process%20in%20Japan.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20not%20like%20a%20bidding%20war%20where%20multiple%20people%20get%20to%20bid%20%E2%80%94%20you%20just%20have%20to%20be%20in%20first%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20before%20image%20of%20the%20main%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65000e8d112d1600192d69af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20before%20image%20of%20the%20main%20room.%20The%20previous%20owner's%20belongings%20were%20left%20behind.%3Cp%3EEric%20McAskill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20entire%20process%2C%20McAskill%20said%20he%20managed%20to%20build%20a%20good%20relationship%20with%20the%20seller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20went%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20and%20it%20took%20about%20a%20month%20or%20so%2C%20just%20emails%20every%20couple%20of%20days.%20Everything%20was%20done%20completely%20in%20Japanese%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20knew%20that%20it%20was%20a%20young%20family%20coming%20in%2C%20so%20he%20was%20like%2C%20'Okay%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20leave%20enough%20bedding%2C%20pots%2C%20pans%2C%20plates%2C%20and%20everything%2C%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20you're%20not%20running%20out%20to%20IKEA%20on%20your%20first%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20McAskill%20added%20of%20extra%20steps%20the%20seller%20took.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20before%20image%20of%20the%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65000e67112d1600192d6988%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20before%20image%20of%20the%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EEric%20McAskill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20location%20was%20a%20big%20part%20of%20why%20McAskill%20purchased%20the%20akiya.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20already%20familiar%20with%20Nozawaonsen%2C%20the%20village%20where%20he%20bought%20his%20akiya%2C%20because%20it%20was%20where%20his%20family%20would%20vacation%20during%20the%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20winter%2C%20for%20skiing%2C%20we%20really%20loved%20the%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20McAskill%20said%20of%20the%20village%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20small%2C%20quaint%20town%20and%20it's%20known%20for%20having%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fonsen-hot-pools-2017-9%5C%22%3Eonsens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20communal%20baths.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20already%20knew%20some%20of%20the%20local%20community%20members%2C%20which%20helped%20ease%20his%20worries%20about%20moving%20to%20a%20foreign%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMcAskill%20paid%203.5%20million%20Japanese%20yen%2C%20or%20about%20%2423%2C600%2C%20for%20his%20akiya.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20he%20made%20an%20offer%20on%20the%20akiya%20in%20March%202021%2C%20it%20wasn't%20until%20September%202022%20%E2%80%94%2018%20months%20later%20%E2%80%94%20that%20he%20finally%20set%20foot%20in%20the%20house.%20The%20delay%20was%20mostly%20caused%20by%20the%20border%20restrictions%20resulting%20from%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20akiya%20that%20has%20one%20side%20of%20the%20building%20blocked%20by%20a%20huge%20pile%20of%20snow.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6507b556cd637c0019c69642%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDuring%20winter%2C%20snow%20gets%20piled%20up%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20akiya.%3Cp%3EEric%20McAskill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMcAskill's%20akiya%20measures%20just%20over%202%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20and%20it%20sits%20on%20a%20plot%20of%20land%20that%20measures%20about%205%2C300%20square%20feet.%20He%20estimates%20that%20the%20house%20is%20at%20least%20150%20years%20old%2C%20because%20one%20of%20the%20previous%20owners%20was%20born%20in%20this%20house%20in%201872.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20first%20floor%20of%20the%20akiya%2C%20there%20are%20three%20bedrooms%2C%20an%20office%2C%20a%20kitchen%2C%20a%20pantry%2C%20and%20two%20utility%20rooms.%20Upstairs%2C%20there%20are%20another%20two%20bedrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20upstairs%2C%20I%20can%20actually%20enter%20into%20a%20part%20of%20the%20roof%20structure%20of%20the%20house%20that's%20from%201872%2C%20where%20it%20has%20the%20traditional%20beams%20and%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20McAskill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20plans%20to%20put%20in%20proper%20flooring%20and%20convert%20the%20space%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20thinking%20I'm%20going%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20games%20room%2C%20put%20a%20ping%20pong%20table%20there%2C%20and%20make%20it%20a%20place%20where%20the%20boys%20can%20hang%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAlthough%20the%20akiya%20had%20been%20sitting%20empty%20for%20a%20year%2C%20it%20was%20in%20good%20condition.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224629%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Old%20wooden%20beams%20that%20hold%20up%20the%20roof%20of%20the%20akiya.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65000e7c112d1600192d699c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223472%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOld%20wooden%20beams%20that%20hold%20up%20the%20roof%20of%20the%20akiya.%3Cp%3EEric%20McAskill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20owner%20had%20died%2C%20but%20family%20members%20have%20been%20coming%20around%20to%20the%20house%20to%20tend%20to%20the%20place%20and%20the%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20very%20fortunate%20that%20way.%20I%20know%20other%20places%20where%20people%20haven't%20stepped%20inside%20in%20years%2C%20and%20they're%20starting%20to%20fall%20apart%2C%20sadly%2C%26quot%3B%20McAskill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20everything%20that%20belonged%20to%20the%20previous%20owner%20was%20also%20left%20to%20the%20McAskills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20first%20came%20here%2C%20I%20spent%20three%20weeks%20just%20cleaning%20the%20house%20%E2%80%94%20deciding%20what%20to%20keep%2C%20what%20not%20to%20keep%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20after%20getting%20rid%20of%20boxes%20and%20boxes%20of%20ceramic%20dishware%2C%20I%20still%20have%20a%20seating%20placement%20where%20I%20could%20feed%2030%20people%20at%20once.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMcAskill%20did%20most%20of%20the%20projects%20himself%2C%20and%20he's%20about%20three-quarters%20through%20the%20akiya%20restoration%20process.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221279%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20a%20protective%20suit%20painting%20the%20walls%20of%20an%20abandoned%20home%20in%20the%20Japanese%20countryside.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6502904c992da60019ec0647%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22956%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcAskill%20painted%20the%20interior%20walls%20of%20the%20akiya.%3Cp%3EEric%20McAskill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20he's%20updated%20the%20heating%20systems%2C%20turned%20the%20water%20on%2C%20repainted%20the%20interiors%2C%20insulated%20the%20attic%2C%20and%20renovated%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20hooked%20up%20to%20the%20grid%2C%20the%20electrical%20system%20in%20the%20house%20was%20very%20old%20and%20had%20to%20be%20updated%20too%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20electricity%20was%20only%20at%2030%20amps%2C%20so%20it%20was%20a%20very%20low%20amount%20of%20electricity%20coming%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20McAskill%20said.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20first%20things%20I%20did%20was%20install%20a%20nice%20heat%20pump%20to%20do%20heating%20and%20cooling%2C%20but%20that%20thing%20needed%20so%20much%20electricity%20that%20every%20time%20in%20the%20winter%20when%20I%20try%20to%20turn%20it%20on%2C%20the%20whole%20house%20would%20just%20crash.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcAskill%20estimates%20he%20has%20spent%20about%20%247%2C400%20on%20renovations%20and%20expects%20to%20spend%20another%20%247%2C400.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221224%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McAskill%20installing%20rock%20wool%20insulation%20in%20the%20dark.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65000e64112d1600192d6984%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22918%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcAskill%20installing%20rock%20wool%20insulation%20in%20the%20dark.%3Cp%3EEric%20McAskill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20say%20that's%20on%20the%20high%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20could%20get%20away%20with%20doing%20it%20for%20cheaper%20because%20I%20can%20do%20some%20of%20the%20work%20myself%2C%20or%20I%20have%20friends%20who%20work%20in%20the%20trades%20here%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20he%20plans%20on%20splurging%20on%20a%20nice%20sauna%20for%20the%20akiya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20probably%20be%20four%20or%20five%20grand%2C%20so%20half%20of%20that%20budget%20will%20be%20the%20sauna%20and%20reclaiming%20the%20rest%20of%20that%20roof%20area.%20That's%20just%20wood%2C%20paint%2C%20tiles%20%E2%80%94%20that%20kind%20of%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMcAskill%20and%20his%20family%20aren't%20living%20in%20the%20akiya%20full-time%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20main%20room%20after%20McAskill%20cleaned%20up%20the%20space.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65000e87112d1600192d69a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20main%20room%20after%20McAskill%20cleaned%20up%20the%20space.%3Cp%3EEric%20McAskill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMcAskill%20and%20his%20wife%20still%20have%20a%20place%20back%20in%20Bali%2C%20where%20they're%20remotely%20managing%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkalimayadiveresort.com%2Fkalimaya-location-sumbawa-indonesia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escuba%20diving%20resort%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20own%20on%20another%20nearby%20Indonesian%20island%2C%20Sumbawa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20not%20Japanese%20residents%20yet%2C%20but%20they're%20going%20to%20make%20their%20move%20permanent%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20is%20to%20move%20here%20permanently%20when%20it%20gets%20more%20to%20be%20like%20my%20kids'%20school%20age%2C%20because%20they%20have%20such%20a%20good%20school%20system%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20McAskill%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20free%20for%20residents%2C%20and%20they%20actually%20give%20a%20Japanese%20tutor%20for%20children%20to%20help%20them%20with%20the%20language.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Japan%2C%20national%20or%20public%20schools%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mofa.go.jp%2Fpolicy%2Fhuman%2Fecono_rep2%2Farticle13.html%5C%22%3Eno%20tuition%20fees%20for%20primary%20and%20lower%20secondary%20education%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20government%20also%20provides%20textbooks%20free%20of%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMcAskill%20says%20the%20local%20community%20has%20also%20been%20very%20welcoming%20towards%20his%20family.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20alternate%20view%20of%20the%20kitchen%20after%20the%20renovation.%20McAskill%20cleaned%20up%20the%20place%20and%20reinstalled%20new%20cabinets%20and%20ceilings.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65000e774717fd0019fc7dce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcAskill%20cleaned%20up%20the%20kitchen%20and%20reinstalled%20new%20cabinets%20and%20ceilings.%20He%20kept%20some%20of%20the%20previous%20owner's%20items.%3Cp%3EEric%20McAskill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20haven't%20had%20to%20go%20to%20the%20store%20to%20buy%20vegetables%20in%20about%20two%20weeks%20because%20our%20neighbors%20are%20all%20harvesting%20their%20fields%2C%20and%20they%20all%20bring%20us%20gifts%2C%26quot%3B%20McAskill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20community%20here%20is%20fantastically%20accepting%2C%20and%20they're%20so%20happy%20to%20have%20children%20back%20in%20the%20community%20as%20well%2C%20because%20Japan%20is%20facing%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fjapan-birthrate-reaches-record-low-billions-spent-2023-6%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFor%2520a%2520seventh%2520consecutive%2520year%252C%2520Japan%2527s%2520birth%2520rate%2520declined%252C%2520dropping%2C%2525%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520or%25201.57%2520million%2520people.%5C%22%3Ecrisis%20of%20declining%20birth%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20countryside%20is%20just%20emptying%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20he%20had%20to%20get%20used%20to%20was%20the%20trash%20disposal%20system%2C%20which%20prioritizes%20recycling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Japan%2C%20people%20have%20to%20sort%20their%20trash%20into%20specific%20categories%20for%20recycling%2C%20McAskill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20different%20colored%20bags%20which%20you%20purchase%20to%20separate%20your%20garbage.%20So%20you'll%20have%20one%20bag%2C%20which%20is%20for%20burnable%20stuff%20like%20papers%20or%20dirty%20food%20items.%20And%20then%20you%20have%20clean%20plastics%20that%20will%20be%20in%20a%20separate%20bag%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221206%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McAskill%20working%20in%20the%20garden.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6507b551cd637c0019c6963b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcAskill%20working%20on%20the%20overgrown%20garden.%3Cp%3EEric%20McAskill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMcAskill%20said%20the%20restoration%20process%20has%20been%20smoother%20than%20he%20expected.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20say%20I've%20been%20lucky.%20I%20expected%20way%20more%20work%20than%20what%20it%20has%20been.%20The%20house%20is%20in%20way%20better%20shape%20than%20I%20would've%20imagined%2C%26quot%3B%20McAskill%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20says%20he's%20only%20doing%20the%20stuff%20he%20knows%20he%20can%20fix%20up%2C%20and%20will%20probably%20bring%20in%20external%20help%20when%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20small%20projects%20around%20the%20house%20that%20have%20been%20more%20challenging%20than%20he%20expected%2C%20but%20it's%20all%20because%20he%20decided%20to%20do%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20in%20my%20kitchen%20renovation%2C%20this%20time%20I%20actually%20tried%20my%20hand%20at%20doing%20traditional%20Japanese%20limestone%20plaster%2C%26quot%3B%20McAskill%20added.%20%26quot%3BThey%20call%20it%20shikkui%20plastering%2C%20and%20so%20it's%20the%20traditional%20earthen%20wall%20method%20of%20plastering%20and%20wow%2C%20that%20is%20difficult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMcAskill%20has%20one%20piece%20of%20advice%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20move%20to%20a%20foreign%20country%3A%20Decide%20what%20matters%20to%20you%20in%20your%20daily%20life.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20renovated%20exterior%20of%20the%20akiya%20that%20McAskill%20bought.%20Although%20it%20was%20considered%20abandoned%2C%20the%20property%20was%20in%20relatively%20good%20shape.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65000e71112d1600192d6992%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20renovated%20exterior%20of%20the%20akiya%20that%20McAskill%20bought.%3Cp%3EEric%20McAskill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPick%20a%20location%2C%20work%20on%20your%20own%20classifications%20of%20what's%20important%20to%20you%20for%20your%20day-to-day%20living%2C%26quot%3B%20McAskill%20said.%20%26quot%3BConvenience%20stores%2C%20schools%2C%20that%20kind%20of%20stuff.%20So%20narrowing%20down%20an%20area%20and%20then%20it's%20just%20visiting%20where%20you%20want%20to%20live%20and%20getting%20to%20know%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20definitely%20challenges%20that%20come%20with%20living%20in%20a%20foreign%20country%20with%20a%20foreign%20culture%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20approach%20them%20with%20an%20open%20mind%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20it's%20not%20easy%2C%20but%20I%20think%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20adventure%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20a%20different%20way%20of%20doing%20things%2C%20and%20it's%20fun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMcAskill%20provided%20Insider%20with%20proof%20of%20his%20house%20purchase.%20He%20was%20not%20able%20to%20share%20receipts%20for%20the%20renovations%20but%20estimated%20to%20the%20best%20of%20his%20ability.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabandoned-home-restoration-diy-foreigner-akiya-japan-family-slow-life-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%2