01024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-657857%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDamaged%20statues%20at%20Maha%20Kal%20Lok%20corridor%20in%20Ujjain%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Photo%3A%20The%20Wire%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20four%20days%20after%20the%20slated%20unveiling%20of%20the%20Adi%20Shankaracharya%20statue%2C%20Modi%20is%20scheduled%20to%20address%20a%20huge%20rally%20in%20Bhopal%20to%20mark%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20five%20Jan%20Ashirvad%20Yatras%20that%20was%20flagged%20off%20by%20three%20senior%20Union%20ministers%20from%20five%20corners%20of%20the%20state%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Statue%20of%20Oneness%E2%80%99%2C%20costing%20Rs%202%2C400%20crore%2C%20is%20dedicated%20to%20the%20eighth-century%20philosopher%2C%20an%20influential%20and%20revered%20figure%20in%20Hinduism.%20Omakareshwar%20is%20a%20temple%20town%20that%20houses%20one%20of%20the%2012%20Jyotirlingas%20dedicated%20to%20Lord%20Shiva.%20The%20state%20government%20is%20estimated%20to%20incur%20an%20expenditure%20of%20hundreds%20of%20crores%20on%20the%20two%20grand%20functions%20aimed%20to%20push%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20agenda%20for%20votes.%20The%20BJP%20has%20made%20massive%20preparations%20to%20mobilise%2010%20lakh%20party%20workers%20for%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20rally%20on%20September%2025%2C%20which%20is%20also%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20its%20ideologue%20Deen%20Dayal%20Upadhyay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDole-outs%20plus%20Hindutva%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20corrosive%20combination%20of%20dole-outs%20and%20extravagant%20show%20of%20Hindutva%20is%20pushing%20the%20debt-ridden%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20bankruptcy%2C%20as%20it%20borrowed%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore%20more%20as%20loan%20this%20month%20in%20two%20tranches%20to%20meet%20perilously%20mounting%20expenses%20owing%20to%20chief%20minister%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20seemingly%20interminable%20promises%20and%20announcements%20to%20the%20voters%20in%20the%20election%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20debt%20burden%20on%20the%20state%20government%20has%20already%20risen%20to%20nearly%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20crore%20and%20likely%20go%20up%20further%20before%20the%20notification%20for%20the%20assembly%20election%20is%20issued%20next%20month.%20Far%20from%20worrying%20about%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20scary%20financial%20health%2C%20chief%20minister%20Chouhan%20looks%20all%20too%20eager%20to%20splurge%20the%20taxpayer%E2%80%99s%20money%20to%20woo%20voters%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20further%20emptying%20the%20state%20exchequer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20huge%20financial%20implications%20of%20its%20promises%20to%20the%20voters%20are%20any%20indication%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20main%20challenger%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20also%20does%20not%20look%20deterred%20by%20the%20dismal%20financial%20scenario%20either%2C%20as%20it%20too%20is%20offering%20dole-outs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeemingly%20unmindful%20of%20the%20disastrous%20impact%20on%20the%20state%20exchequer%20of%20the%20pre-poll%20sops%2C%20they%20have%20promised%20%E2%80%93%20and%20keep%20on%20promising%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20blithely%20competing%20with%20each%20other%20to%20woo%20the%20voters%2C%20as%20though%20they%20wield%20some%20magic%20wand%20whose%20spell%20will%20automatically%20salvage%20the%20financial%20condition%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%20the%20state%20is%20still%20two%20months%20away%2C%20both%20parties%20have%20promised%20schemes%20totaling%20thousands%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20look%20done%20with%20the%20promising%20spree%20yet.%20The%20%E2%80%9CRevdi%20culture%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20state%20is%20in%20full%20play%2C%20notwithstanding%20its%20criticism%20by%20the%20BJP%20central%20leadership%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20defends%20giveaways%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20Kamal%20Nath%20says%20the%20party%20will%20fulfill%20its%20promises%20by%20adopting%20necessary%20fiscal%20prudence%20which%20is%20sorely%20lacking%20in%20the%20BJP%20government.%20The%20Congress%20veteran%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20spending%20on%20welfare%20schemes%20is%20one%20thing%20and%20splurging%20on%20events%20is%20quite%20another.%20The%20Congress%20has%20already%20worked%20out%20the%20required%20arithmetic%20of%20raising%20funds%20to%20meet%20the%20expenses%20that%20will%20be%20incurred%20in%20fulfilling%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20promises%2C%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20the%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20chief%20avers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F27124135%2Fthewire2.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F27124135%2Fthewire2.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F27124135%2Fthewire2-300x158.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F27124135%2Fthewire2-1024x538.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-488428%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20photo%20of%20Kamal%20Nath.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShivraj%20government%20is%20continuously%20pushing%20the%20state%20into%20the%20quagmire%20of%20debt.%20The%20government%20is%20blowing%20away%20the%20hard-earned%20public%20money%20on%20events%2C%20functions%2C%20self-promotion%2C%20and%20glorification%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Congress%20veteran%2C%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20borrowed%20money%20liberally%20from%20financial%20institutions%20to%20fund%20big%20construction%20projects%20without%20ascertaining%20their%20viability%20and%20with%20the%20sole%20aim%20of%20awarding%20contracts%20to%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20favourite%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%20leaders%20prospered%20over%20the%20years%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9840%25%20commission%20government%E2%80%99%20from%20gobbling%20huge%20money%20as%20commission%20from%20big%20contractors%20in%20lieu%20of%20government%20contracts%2C%E2%80%9D%20alleges%20Kamal%20Nath.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcentral-bjp-leadership-takes-control-of-madhya-pradesh-campaign-and-has-a-bumpy-road-ahead%5C%22%3ECentral%20BJP%20Leadership%20Takes%20Control%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Campaign%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Has%20a%20Bumpy%20Road%20Ahead%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20Tarun%20Bhanot%2C%20who%20was%20the%20finance%20minister%20in%20Kamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%2015-month%20government%2C%20says%20during%20his%2015-month%20government%2C%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%20initiated%20several%20reforms%2C%20and%20multiple%20revenue%20resources%20were%20created%20without%20putting%20any%20extra%20burden%20on%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20alleges%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20claims%20it%20borrowed%20loans%20from%20banks%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20people%2C%20while%20the%20situation%20is%20quite%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20debt%20during%20Digvijay%20Singh-led%20Congress%20government%20was%20at%20Rs%2026%2C000%20crore%20when%20the%20Congress%20chief%20minister%20demitted%20office%2C%20but%20now%20it%20has%20reached%20close%20to%20Rs%204%20lakh%20crore%2C%20and%20the%20financial%20condition%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20state%20continues%20to%20worsen%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Bhanot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EState%20stares%20at%20bankruptcy%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20brazenness%20with%20which%20chief%20minister%20Chouhan%20is%20pursuing%20the%20%E2%80%9Crevdi%20culture%E2%80%9D%20has%20lent%20more%20credence%20to%20the%20speculation%20that%20this%20election%20might%20be%20his%20swan%20song.%20The%20BJP%20central%20leadership%20has%20already%20dropped%20strong%20hints%20that%20even%20if%20the%20party%20returns%20to%20power%2C%20Chouhan%20will%20not%20be%20repeated%2C%20given%20that%20he%20has%20already%20held%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post%20since%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeculations%20are%20rife%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20both%20within%20the%20BJP%20and%20out%20of%20it%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20pre-poll%20bonanzas%20to%20all%20sections%20of%20voters%20betray%20a%20sort%20of%20scorched%20earth%20policy%20%E2%80%93%20a%20military%20strategy%20that%20aims%20to%20destroy%20anything%20that%20might%20be%20useful%20to%20the%20enemy%2C%20which%20usually%20includes%20obvious%20weapons%2C%20transport%20vehicles%2C%20communication%20sites%2C%20and%20industrial%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20scorched%20earth%20policy%20might%20sound%20too%20incongruent%20or%20farfetched%20to%20describe%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20penchant%20for%20mercilessly%20dipping%20into%20exchequer%20but%20statistics%20seem%20to%20suggest%20this%20might%20be%20the%20case%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDebt%20burden%20on%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20risen%20by%20over%2012%25%20in%20the%20last%20one%20year.%20This%20means%20every%20MP%20citizen%20has%20a%20debt%20of%20Rs%2041%2C%20000%20on%20his%20or%20her%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20per%20capita%20debt%20in%20MP%20was%20estimated%20at%20Rs%2013%2C853%20by%20the%20end%20of%20March%202016%2C%20compared%20to%20Rs%2010%2C896%20recorded%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202013-14.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20April%20this%20year%2C%20the%20government%20has%20taken%20loans%20of%20around%20Rs%209%2C000%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20including%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore%20in%20September%2C%20Rs%202000%20crore%20in%20May%2C%20and%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20pre-poll%20announcements%20and%20schemes%20in%20the%20past%20few%20months%20are%20estimated%20to%20increase%20the%20expenditure%20of%20the%20MP%20government%20by%20at%20least%2010%25%20by%20the%20time%20the%20state%20election%20is%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20government%E2%80%99s%20average%20monthly%20expenses%2C%20now%20around%20Rs%2022%2C000%20crore%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20get%20close%20to%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20due%20to%20a%20slew%20of%20pre-poll%20bonanzas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20major%20heads%20of%20the%20increased%20expenditure%2C%20Ladli%20Behna%20Yojana%20alone%20will%20cause%20an%20extra%20burden%20of%20around%20Rs%201%2C500%20crore%20per%20month.%20This%20estimate%20is%20for%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20targeted%20beneficiary%20and%20this%20could%20go%20up%20to%20three%20folds%20if%20the%20chief%20minister%20keeps%20his%20promise%20to%20raise%20the%20amount%20from%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20Rs%203%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20budget%20has%20allocated%20Rs%208%2C000%20crore%20for%20the%20Ladli%20Behana%20scheme%20for%20which%20close%20to%20Rs%201%2C500%20crore%20is%20required%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20has%20been%20launched%20to%20counter%20the%20similar%20one%20announced%20by%20the%20Congress%20which%20has%20offered%20a%20Rs%201%2C500%20allowance%20to%20women%20if%20voted%20to%20power.%20The%20chief%20minister%20has%20promised%20to%20raise%20the%20amount%20from%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20in%20the%20future.%20There%20are%201.2%20crore%20eligible%20candidates%20for%20the%20scheme%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDoubling%20the%20honorarium%20of%20guest%20teachers%20up%20to%20Rs%2050%2C000%20per%20month%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20yearly%20expense%20of%20Rs%20470%20crore.%20The%20decision%20to%20give%20cooking%20gas%20refills%20to%20Ladli%20Behna%20and%20Ujjwala%20beneficiaries%20at%20Rs%20450%20per%20cylinder%20will%20likely%20cost%20the%20government%20Rs%20100%20crore%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20the%20government%20has%20hiked%20the%20pay%20of%20Anganwadi%20workers%20from%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20Rs%2013%2C000%2C%20doubled%20the%20honorarium%20of%20Rozgar%20Sahayaks%20(from%20Rs%209%2C000%20to%20Rs%2018%2C000)%20and%20tripled%20the%20honorarium%20of%20district%20panchayat%20president%2C%20vice-president%2C%20district%20president%2C%20vice-president%20and%20deputy%20sarpanch%20and%20panch.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20promise%20of%20e-scooters%20to%20meritorious%20students%20will%20cost%20Rs%20135%20crore%20and%20that%20of%20laptops%20for%2078%2C000%20students%20will%20cost%20Rs%20196%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20government%20has%20brought%20contractual%20employees%20at%20par%20with%20regular%20government%20employees%20in%20salary%20and%20other%20facilities.%20This%20will%20have%20substantial%20financial%20implications.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20new%20promises%20being%20made%20almost%20every%20day%20and%20likely%20to%20continue%20till%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20comes%20into%20force%20next%20month%2C%20the%20strain%20on%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20finances%20will%20continue%20to%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20state%20finance%20department%2C%20the%20overall%20debt%20of%20MP%20as%20on%20March%2031%2C%202022%20was%20Rs%202.95%20lakh%20crore.%20State%20finance%20minister%20Jagdish%20Devra%20told%20the%20state%20assembly%20in%20June%20this%20year%20that%20from%20June%2030%2C%202022%20to%20February%201%2C%202023%2C%20the%20state%20government%20took%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2016%2C000%20crore%20in%20several%20installments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20government%20has%20taken%20an%20additional%20loan%20of%20Rs%2013%2C000%20crore%20in%20several%20tranches%20and%20is%20planning%20to%20take%20more%20to%20meet%20the%20expenses%20that%20its%20please-all%20announcements%20in%20the%20election%20year%20have%20entailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20women%2C%20the%20state%20allocated%20Rs%20358%20crore%20to%20expand%20and%20establish%20four%20temples%3A%20Devilok%20in%20Salkanpur%2C%20Ramlok%20in%20Orchha%2C%20Ravidas%20Samark%20in%20Sagar%2C%20and%20Divya%20Vanvasi%20Lok%20in%20Chitrakoot.%C2%A0%C2%A0The%20cost%20of%20development%20of%20these%20temples%20has%20gone%20manifold%20from%20the%20budgetary%20allocation.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20Ravidas%20temple%20in%20Sagar%2C%20whose%20Bhumi%20pujan%20was%20performed%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20last%20month%2C%20is%20being%20constructed%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20cost%20of%20the%20temple%20expansion%20and%20construction%20projects%20and%20other%20assorted%20religious%20allurements%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20hiking%20honorarium%20of%20temple%20priests%2C%20free%20travel%20for%20pilgrim%20centres%2C%20freeing%20temple%20land%20from%20government%20control%2C%20etc%20%E2%80%93%20announced%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20recent%20months%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20around%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20source%20of%20major%20drain%20of%20the%20state%20exchequer%20is%20publicity%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20in%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20government%20had%20spent%20about%20Rs%20753%20crore%20on%20advertisements%20in%20print%20and%20electronic%20media%20during%20a%20period%20of%2034%20months%20preceding%20the%20assembly%20elections%20held%20in%20November%202018%2C%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20veritable%20media%20blitzkrieg%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20coming%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20may%20have%20already%20spent%20many%20times%20more%20money%20on%20advertisements%20than%20it%20did%20in%202018.%20For%20over%20six%20months%2C%20not%20a%20day%20has%20passed%20without%20the%20MP%20government%20having%20occupied%20substantial%20space%20in%20print%20and%20electronic%20media%20to%20blow%20its%20trumpets.%20There%20is%20no%20accounting%2C%20of%20course%2C%20of%20the%20money%20it%20is%20spending%20on%20digital%20media%20and%20the%20personal%20gratification%20of%20journalists%20and%20social%20media%20influencers.%20Together%2C%20they%20form%20a%20strong%20support%20base%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Frakesh-dixit%5C%22%3ERakesh%20Dixit%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Bhopal-based%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695259821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F22125141%2FScreen-Shot-2018-09-22-at-12.50.51-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fshivraj-singhs-profligacy-in-poll-year-brings-debt-ridden-mp-to-the-brink-of-bankruptcy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20debt%20burden%20on%20the%20state%20is%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20crore%20and%20likely%20go%20up%20further%20before%20the%20notification%20for%20the%20assembly%20election%20is%20issued%20next%20month.%20Both%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%2C%20unmindful%20of%20state's%20financial%20situation%2C%20are%20promising%20moon%20to%20the%20voters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fshivraj-singhs-profligacy-in-poll-year-brings-debt-ridden-mp-to-the-brink-of-bankruptcy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20offers%20work%20permits%20to%20half%20million%20Venezuelans%20already%20in%20country%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695258847000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103822633%2Cimgsize-25320.cms%22%2