https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5a576da3a75e20b0378b4985%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221371%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai.%3Cp%3EBeck%20Diefenbach%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20recent%20Google%20Search%20update%20is%20causing%20anger%20across%20the%20web.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20site%20owners%20say%20they%20are%20being%20pushed%20down%20in%20results%20with%20huge%20drops%20in%20traffic.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20recently%20tweaked%20its%20guidelines%20to%20permit%20AI-generated%20content.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Overholt%20saw%20half%20of%20her%20website's%20traffic%20disappear%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20joke%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20person%20wrote%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.webmasterworld.com%2Fgoogle%2F5093320-1-50.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20forum%20for%20website%20owners%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI've%20got%20long-form%20content%2C%20well%20written%2C%20well%20researched%2C%20filled%20with%20original%20image%20content%20LOSING%20to%20500%20word%20AI%20generated%20crap%E2%80%A6Google%20is%20apparently%20forcing%20publishers%20to%20generate%20AI%20spam%20or%20die.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20are%20just%20two%20voices%20in%20a%20chorus%20complaining%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.google.com%2Fsearch%2Fupdates%2Fhelpful-content-update%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20latest%20%26quot%3Bhelpful%20content%26quot%3B%20update%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20meant%20to%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20search%20results%20%E2%80%93%20has%20sent%20their%20websites%20tumbling%20down%20the%20rankings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20update%2C%20which%20has%20been%20rolling%20out%20this%20month%2C%20promised%20several%20positive%20tweaks%20to%20punish%20pages%20that%20are%20built%20only%20to%20rank%20well%20in%20search%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20also%20came%20with%20a%20big%20red%20flag%20that%20currently%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20website%20owners%20worried%3A%20human%20authorship%20is%20no%20longer%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frustybrick%2Fstatus%2F1702436607758930371%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAs%20spotted%20by%20SEO%20Roundtable's%20Barry%20Schwartz%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Google%20recently%20tweaked%20the%20documentation%20explaining%20how%20it%20defines%20%26quot%3Bhelpful%20content.%26quot%3B%20No%20longer%20is%20it%20%26quot%3Bhelpful%20content%20written%20%3Cem%3Eby%20people%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20for%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20simply%2C%20%26quot%3BHelpful%20content%20written%20for%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20of%20that%20change%2C%20which%20coincided%20with%20the%20latest%20Search%20algorithm%20update%2C%20has%20made%20many%20website%20owners%20nervous%20about%20what's%20to%20come.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20travel%20blogger%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fellerosetweets%2Fstatus%2F1704433491499176173%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20she%20watched%2080%25%20of%20her%20traffic%20disappear%20in%20the%20space%20of%2048%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20posts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fellerosetweets%2Fstatus%2F1704457231675085090%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bvery%20obviously%20AI%20written%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20outranking%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%20we%20saw%2055%25%20drop%20from%20normal%20traffic%2C%20today%20it's%20even%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20Overholt%2C%20who%20runs%20several%20travel-related%20websites%2C%20told%20Insider.%20She%20watched%20pages%20that%20previously%20ranked%20first%20for%20certain%20terms%20tumble%20to%20fifth%2C%20sixth%2C%20or%20seventh%20place%20in%20Google%20search%20results.%20Web%20pages%20that%20are%20three%20or%20four%20years%20old%20now%20rank%20above%20her%2C%20she%20added.%20(%3Cspan%3EOverholt%20has%20written%20freelance%20articles%20for%20Insider%20in%20the%20past).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFluctuations%20are%20common%20when%20Google%20pushes%20out%20new%20updates%2C%20and%20content%20creators%20often%20complain%20when%20important%20things%20like%20this%20change.%20But%20some%20website%20owners%20claim%20they've%20never%20seen%20a%20shift%20like%20this%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAI%20content%20and%20'rehashing'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EThe%20helpful%20content%20ranking%20system%20was%20designed%20to%20show%20more%20content%20in%20search%20results%20that's%20created%20to%20help%20or%20inform%20people%2C%20and%20less%20content%20created%20solely%20to%20rank%20better%20on%20Google%20Search%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20targeting%20content%20produced%20by%20any%20particular%20method%20%E2%80%93%20AI%20or%20otherwise%20%E2%80%93%20we're%20concerned%20with%20the%20quality%20of%20a%20given%20webpage%20and%20its%20helpfulness%20to%20readers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20major%20goal%20seems%20to%20be%20to%20demote%20sites%20that%20reuse%20and%20rejig%20information%20that's%20already%20online%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20ranking%20higher%20in%20Search%20results.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-killing-web-grand-bargain-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge%20language%20models%20are%20trained%20on%20masses%20of%20content%3C%2Fa%3E%20that's%20been%20scraped%20from%20the%20public%20internet.%20So%2C%20in%20essence%2C%20these%20AI%20models%20are%20cleverly%20rehashing%20what's%20already%20been%20published.%20That%20should%20be%20something%20Google%20punishes.%20Although%2C%20the%20company%20is%20also%20developing%20its%20own%20AI%20models%20that%20do%20similar%20things%2C%20so%20it's%20conflicted%20here.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Search%20advocate%20John%20Mueller%20spent%20the%20day%20trying%20to%20calm%20some%20website%20owners%20down%2C%20while%20explaining%20the%20goals%20of%20the%20company's%20recent%20update.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20debated%20with%20one%20website%20owner%20back%20and%20forth%20over%20their%20website%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20the%20net%20worth%20of%20celebrities.%20Schwartz%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seroundtable.com%2Fgoogle-compilation-chatgpt-output-content-36055.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20the%20details%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Search%20Engine%20Roundtable%20on%20Wednesday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMueller's%20response%20shows%20what%20a%20tricky%20situation%20Google%20finds%20itself%20in.%20One%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20company%20is%20saying%20AI%20content%20is%20OK%2C%20but%20on%20the%20other%2C%20Mueller%20is%20criticizing%20a%20site%20owner%20for%20using%20ChatGPT.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20should%20focus%20on%20unique%2C%20compelling%2C%20high-quality%20content%20that%20adds%20to%20the%20web%2C%26quot%3B%20Mueller%20wrote%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BAs%20you%20have%20it%20now%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20a%20compilation%20of%20ChatGPT%20output%20on%20topics%20that%20tons%20of%20sites%20have%20already%20covered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%2C%20Mueller%20addressed%20similar%20issues%20during%20a%20Reddit%20chat.%20One%20comment%20stood%20out%20as%20an%20inadvertent%20condemnation%20of%20Google's%20own%20AI%20model%20efforts%2C%20which%20include%20pitching%20newsrooms%20on%20having%20its%20machines%20write%20stories%20automatically.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20definition%20(I'm%20simplifying)%2C%20if%20you're%20using%20AI%20to%20write%20your%20content%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20rehashed%20from%20other%20sites%2C%26quot%3B%20Mueller%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESpotting%20AI%20content%20is%20impossible%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20how%20much%20of%20the%20content%20that%20has%20been%20bumped%20up%20is%20AI-generated%2C%20or%20whether%20this%20is%20just%20other%20content%20written%20differently%20by%20humans.%20That%20underscores%20a%20problem%20for%20both%20users%20and%20Google%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-cant-identify-ai-generated-text-bad-for-internet-models-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIt's%20currently%20impossible%20to%20spot%20the%20difference%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20machine-generated%20content%20and%20human%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20continues%20to%20say%20that%20content%20built%20entirely%20for%20the%20purpose%20or%20ranking%20high%20in%20search%20results%20will%20be%20punished.%20But%20the%20company%20no%20longer%20says%20it's%20blocking%20AI%20content%20from%20getting%20through%2C%20as%20long%20as%20it%20appears%20to%20pass%20quality%20tests%20run%20by%20Google's%20own%20bots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20battle%20that%20the%20company%20will%20be%20fighting%20on%20multiple%20fronts.%20Generative%20AI%20is%20making%20content%20creation%20much%20easier%20and%20faster.%20That%20is%20likely%20to%20trigger%20a%20flood%20of%20machine-generated%20content%20on%20the%20web.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPicking%20out%20which%20AI-powered%20blog%20or%20image%20is%20better%20than%20another%20one%2C%20amongst%20thousands%20on%20the%20same%20subject%20%E2%80%94%20all%20automatically%20published%20within%20a%20few%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20a%20herculean%20task%2C%20even%20for%20a%20tech%20company%20as%20savvy%20as%20Google.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAn%20AI%20'tank%20man'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20publication%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.404media.co%2Ffirst-google-search-result-for-tiananmen-square-tank-man-is-ai-generated-selfie%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E404%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20a%20search%20for%20the%20Tiananmen%20Square%20%26quot%3Btank%20man%26quot%3B%20was%20recently%20returning%20an%20AI-generated%20version%20of%20the%20iconic%20image.%20Insider%20was%20unable%20to%20replicate%20it%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjosephfcox%2Fstatus%2F1704484390573646188%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DqXeQ5wkxERk2ASthsfwBVQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseveral%20other%20people%20corroborated%20404's%20findings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20suggesting%20that%20Google%20made%20some%20changes%20after%20404%20published%20its%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Google%20has%20served%20up%20an%20AI%20version%20of%20a%20well-known%20piece%20of%20digital%20content.%20Last%20May%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffuturism.com%2Ftop-google-result-johannes-vermeer-ai-generated-knockoff%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFuturism%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20top%20result%20for%20%26quot%3BJohannes%20Vermeer%26quot%3B%20was%20an%20AI-generated%20version%20of%20The%20Girl%20With%20the%20Pearl%20Earring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20images%20and%20video%2C%20there%20may%20be%20ways%20to%20tackle%20the%20problem%3A%20Google%20and%20others%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F8%2F29%2F23849107%2Fsynthid-google-deepmind-ai-image-detector%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eare%20building%20ways%20to%20watermark%20images%20and%20video%20that%20are%20AI-generated%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20could%20help%20search%20engines%20detect%20them.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20latest%20changes%20have%20many%20people%20nervous%20that%20the%20AI%20content%20flood%20has%20begun%20and%20Google%20is%20letting%20it%20flow%20with%20few%20guardrails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20Google%20employee%3F%20Got%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20reporter%20Hugh%20Langley%20using%20encrypted%20messaging%20apps%20Signal%20or%20Telegram%20at%20%2B1%20(628)%20228-1836.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blan