0who%20have%20generated%20100%2C000%20video%20views%20in%20the%20previous%2030-day%20period.%20TikTok%20told%20Insider%20it%20considers%20factors%20like%20video%20view%20counts%2C%20video%20engagement%2C%20and%20the%20location%20in%20which%20a%20video%20was%20seen%2C%20when%20determining%20Creator%20Fund%20payouts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20how%20much%20six%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-money-tiktokers-earn-from-creator-fund-daily-rates-2022-8%3Fr%3Dtiktok-views-lp%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Ecreators%20have%20earned%20through%20the%20Creator%20Fund%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok's%20%241%20billion%20target%20is%20small%20compared%20to%20YouTube's%20overall%20creator%20payouts.%20YouTube's%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.youtube%2Finside-youtube%2Fletter-from-susan-our-2021-priorities%2F%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021%20that%20the%20company%20had%20paid%20%2430%20billion%20to%20creators%2C%20artists%2C%20and%20media%20companies%20over%20a%20three-year%20time%20frame.%20It%20also%20set%20up%20a%20%24100%20million%20fund%20in%202021%2C%20meant%20to%20last%20through%202022%2C%20specifically%20for%20its%20TikTok-like%20feature%2C%20shorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20platforms%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnapchat-decreases-amount-of-money-paid-to-influencers-via-spotlight-2022-10%3Fr%3Dtiktok-views-lp%5C%22%3ESnapchat%20have%20paid%20influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20to%20incentivize%20them%20to%20create%20short%20videos.%20Instagram%20also%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-money-instagram-paid-creator-reels-bonus-2021-12%3Fr%3Dtiktok-views-lp%5C%22%3Epaid%20some%20creators%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20the%20number%20of%20views%20their%20reels%20generate%2C%20offering%20%26quot%3Bbonuses%26quot%3B%20for%20hitting%20certain%20short-video%20view%20thresholds%2C