0TikTok%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20July%202022%20that%20the%20company%20understood%20%26quot%3Bhow%20important%20it%20is%20that%20our%20creators%20are%20appreciated%20for%20their%20work%20and%20look%20to%20our%20creator%20community%20for%20valuable%20feedback%20to%20better%20serve%20their%20needs.%26quot%3B%20They%20pointed%20to%20other%20monetization%20features%20like%20live%20subscriptions%20that%20are%20available%20to%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20more%20about%20how%20much%20creators%20have%20earned%20through%20the%20Creator%20Fund%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-influencer-earnings-for-views-compared-to-youtube-creator-fund-2020-8%3Fr%3Dtiktok-views-lp%5C%22%3ETikTok%20influencers%20reveal%20how%20much%20money%20they're%20getting%20paid%20from%20its%20%241%20billion%20Creator%20Fund%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20pennies%20per%20thousand%20views%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-creators-like-mrbeast-making-from-tiktok-creator-fund-2022-1%3Fr%3Dtiktok-views-lp%5C%22%3EHank%20Green%20(7.9%20million%20followers)%20and%20MrBeast%20(87.3%20million%20followers)%20share%20how%20much%20they've%20earned%20from%20the%20Creator%20Fund%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-money-tiktok-pays-creator-fund-1-million-followers-2022-1%3Fr%3Dtiktok-views-lp%5C%22%3ELifestyle%20influencer%20Victoria%20Paris%20(about%201.9%20million%20followers)%20discloses%20her%20monthly%20Creator%20Fund%20earnings%20from%20February%20to%20December%202021%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-money-tiktoker-makes-with-1-million-followers-2021-8%3Fr%3Dtiktok-views-lp%5C%22%3EVi%20Luong%20(about%20986%2C000%20followers)%20shares%20her%20monthly%20earnings%20from%20the%20Creator%20Fund%20and%20brand%20deals%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%