%20could%20buy%20ads%20alongside%20%26quot%3Bthe%20top%204%25%26quot%3B%20of%20content%20in%20different%20categories%20like%20fashion%2C%20cooking%2C%20and%20beauty.%20It%20agreed%20to%20split%20half%20of%20the%20revenue%20with%20the%20creator%20whose%20video%20appeared%20before%20the%20in-feed%20ad.%20Only%20creators%20with%20at%20least%20100%2C000%20followers%20qualify%20for%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20more%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-to-share-half-ad-revenue-with-creators-pulse-program-2022-5%3Fr%3Dtiktok-views-lp%5C%22%3Ehow%20TikTok%20Pulse%20compares%20to%20other%20ad%20revenue-sharing%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20creators%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.tiktok.com%2Fen-us%2Fpulse-premiere%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%202023%20it%20was%20also%20testing%20a%20version%20of%20the%20Pulse%20program%20for%20traditional%20media%20publishers%20called%20Pulse%20Premiere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20the%20Creator%20Fund%2C%20initial%20payments%20from%20TikTok%20Pulse%20have%20been%20underwhelming%2C%20creators%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-pulse-ad-revenue-share-payments-creators-2022-11%3Fr%3Dtiktok-views-lp%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Ehow%20much%20gaming%20and%20lifestyle%20creators%20have%20earned%20from%20Pulse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20the%20creators%20who%20shared%20payment%20data%20with%20Insider%20saw%20Pulse%20RPMs%20in%20the%20%247%20to%20%248%20range%2C%20one%20creator%20reported%20an%20RPM%20closer%20to%20%243.%20The%20creator%20RPMs%20were%20competitive%20on%20TikTok%20Pulse%20when%20compared%20to%20other%20ad-revenue%20solutions%20like%20YouTube's%20partner%20program%20for%20long-form%20video%2C%20but%20the%20revenue-generating%2