question%20at%20an%20interaction%20organised%20by%20Ananta%20Aspen%20Centre.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGarcetti%20said%20that%20the%20US%20and%20India%20had%20gone%20through%20rocky%20patches%20like%20the%201971%20war.%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20had%20also%20been%20a%20perception%20in%20the%20US%20that%20India%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20international%20order%20on%20nuclear%20proliferation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCanada%20is%20a%20dear%20friend%2C%20ally%2C%20partner%20and%20neighbour%E2%80%A6%20w%3C%2Fspan%3Ee%20happen%20to%20care%20deeply%20for%20Canada%20just%20as%20we%20care%20deeply%20for%20India%3Cspan%3E.%20And%20I%20think%20that%20moments%20like%20this%20don%E2%80%99t%20define%20our%20relationship.%20But%20they%20certainly%20can%20slow%20down%20progress.%20And%20they%E2%80%99re%20gut%20checks%20for%20everybody%20to%20say%20how%20do%20we%20interact%20with%20each%20other%3F%20What%20do%20we%20stand%20for%3F%20How%20do%20we%20enforce%20ideas%20like%20sovereignty%20and%20international%20law%3F%20And%20what%20are%20our%20responsibilities%20to%20one%20another%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20Los%20Angeles%20mayor%20pointed%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9Cany%20allegations%20like%20this%20should%20be%20troubling%20to%20anyone%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20with%20an%20active%20criminal%20investigation%2C%20I%20hope%20that%20we%20can%20make%20sure%20that%20perpetrators%20are%20brought%20to%20justice%20and%20that%20we%20can%20all%20allow%20the%20space%20for%20that%20information%20and%20that%20investigation%20to%20occur%20before%20anybody%20leaps%20to%20judgment.%20And%20to%20me%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20most%20important%20role%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Garcetti.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20underlined%20that%20to%20%E2%80%9Ceach%20one%20of%20us%2C%20sovereignty%20is%20a%20very%20important%20principle%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20US%20could%20mediate%20in%20this%20diplomatic%20spat%2C%20he%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cway%20too%20early.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20certainly%20have%20a%20deep%20respect%20and%20huge%20agenda%20and%20relationship%20here.%20And%20us%20having%20a%20relationship%20speaks%20for%20itself.%20We%20share%20our%20border%20we%20share%20so%20much%20history%20and%20culture%20together%20and%20the%20values.%20I%20think%2C%20for%20us%2C%20it%20is%20critical%20for%20us%20to%20return%20the%20three%20principles%20%E2%80%93%20sovereignty%2C%20non-interference%20to%20allow%20the%20criminal%20justice%20investigations%20to%20be%20carried%20out%2C%20And%20then%20there%E2%80%99ll%20be%20accountability%20for%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20another%20query%20whether%20there%20was%20a%20mismatch%20between%20India%20and%20the%20West%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20democratic%20principles%20and%20incitement%20of%20violence%2C%20the%20US%20envoy%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20take%20the%20safety%20of%20Indian%20diplomats%20seriously.%E2%80%9D%20He%20also%20added%20that%20violence%20is%20not%20freedom%20of%20expression.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695230454000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F07103531%2FF0XfRHUWAAo8zAP.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fus-calls-on-india-join-canada-investigation-nijjar-killing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20White%20House%20also%20denied%20a%20media%20report%20which%20claimed%20that%20the%20US%20had%20rebuffed%20a%20Canadian%20proposal%20for%20a%20joint%20statement%20from%20its%20allies%20on%20the%20Indian%20government's%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20murder.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fus-calls-on-india-join-canada-investigation-nijjar-killing%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha%20Passes%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20Confirms%20Implementation%20Not%20Before%202029%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F28095145%2FFxLei4UXgAI-cqM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20September%2020%2C%20passed%20the%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Twenty-eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20that%20seeks%20to%20provide%2033%25%20reservation%20to%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20legislative%20assemblies.%20Most%20opposition%20parties%20supported%20the%20Bill%20in%20principle%20but%20questioned%20the%20delimitation%20clause%20tied%20to%20the%20legislation%20and%20reiterated%20their%20demand%20for%20sub-quotas%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20caste.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20works%20for%2027%20years%2C%20was%20passed%20with%20a%202%2F3rds%20majority%20%E2%80%93%20with%20454%20members%20voting%20in%20favour%20and%20two%20members%20from%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20voting%20against%20it.%20The%20debate%20lasted%20over%20seven%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20and%20saw%20over%2060%20MPs%20speaking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20states%20that%20one-third%20of%20seats%20will%20be%20reserved%20for%20women%20in%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20by%20amending%20Article%20239AA%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20amending%20Article%20330%2C%20and%20in%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%20by%20amending%20Article%20332.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpposition%20members%2C%20while%20pledging%20their%20support%20to%20the%20legislation%2C%20questioned%20the%20need%20to%20tie%20it%20with%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%2C%20which%20is%20to%20be%20conducted%20after%20the%20next%20population%20census%20%E2%80%93%20for%20which%20there%20is%20no%20timeline%20yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20during%20the%20debate%2C%20confirmed%20that%20the%20legislation%20will%20not%20be%20implemented%20before%202029.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20delimitation%20commission%20includes%20representatives%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20political%20parties%20and%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judges%20among%20others%20who%20are%20linked%20to%20election%20procedures.%20If%201%2F3rd%20of%20seats%20have%20to%20be%20reserved%2C%20who%20will%20decide%20on%20these%20seats%3F%20Those%20who%20are%20saying%20why%20aren%E2%80%99t%20you%20doing%20it%3F%20My%20question%20is%20who%20will%20do%20it%3F%20If%20we%20do%20it%20you%20will%20call%20it%20political%20reservation%2C%20if%20Wayanad%20becomes%20a%20reserved%20constituency%20or%20if%20Owaisi%E2%80%99s%20Hyderabad%20becomes%20reserved.%20This%20is%20why%20the%20delimitation%20commission%20which%20conducts%20quasi-judicial%20proceedings%20by%20visiting%20every%20constituency%20(does%20this%20exercise)%20in%20an%20open%20and%20transparent%20manner.%20The%20only%20reason%20behind%20the%20delimitation%20clause%20is%20efficiency%2C%20so%20no%20sides%20are%20taken%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20people%20are%20saying%20on%20social%20media%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20support%20the%20legislation%20now%20because%20it%20will%20not%20be%20implemented%20after%20the%20next%20elections%20due%20to%20the%20delimitation%20exercise.%20Some%20people%20are%20saying%20there%20is%20no%20OBC%20reservation%20or%20Muslim%20reservation%20so%20don%E2%80%99t%20support%20the%20Bill.%20I%20would%20say%20that%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20support%20the%20Bill%2C%20will%20the%20reservations%20come%20sooner%3F%20It%20will%20still%20come%20after%202029.%20Give%20your%20support%2C%20then%20there%20will%20be%20a%20guarantee%20and%20then%20whichever%20government%20comes%20will%20bring%20in%20any%20changes%20that%20may%20be%20needed.%20Let%20the%20process%20begin%E2%80%A6%20There%20will%20be%20no%20delay.%20Soon%20after%20the%20elections%2C%20delimitation%20will%20be%20done%2C%20the%20census%20will%20be%20conducted%20and%20soon%20that%20day%20will%20come%20when%20a%20third%20of%20the%20seats%20are%20reserved%20for%20women%20in%20this%20house.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20also%20sought%20to%20deny%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20the%20legislation%20was%20timed%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20general%20election%20as%20a%20poll%20gimmick.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20some%20parties%2C%20women%20empowerment%20may%20be%20a%20political%20agenda%20and%20a%20political%20issue%20and%20a%20political%20tool%20to%20win%20elections%2C%20but%20for%20BJP%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%20is%20not%20a%20political%20issue%20but%20a%20question%20of%20recognition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25203412%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-8.33.25-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25203412%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-8.33.25-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25203412%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-8.33.25-PM-300x144.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25203412%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-8.33.25-PM-1024x492.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665083%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22577%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFILE%20IMAGE%3A%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20speaks%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20via%20Sansad%20TV%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOpposition%20questions%20delimitation%20clause%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20demanded%20that%20the%20Bill%20be%20implemented%20immediately%20instead%20of%20waiting%20for%20delimitation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPass%20this%20Bill%20today%20itself.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20for%20delimitation%20and%20census.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20for%20it.%20Just%20give%2033%25%20reservation%20to%20women%20and%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census.%20Release%20the%20caste%20census%20data%20that%20was%20conducted%20by%20us%20and%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%2C%20we%20will%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20also%20questioned%20the%20need%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20delimitation%20exercise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMahua%20Moitra%20said%20that%20within%20her%20party%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%2C%20women%20already%20constituted%2037%25%20of%20the%20MPs.%20The%20Bill%20should%20be%20renamed%20as%20%E2%80%9CWomen%E2%80%99s%20Rescheduling%20Bill.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20this%20government%20wanted%20to%20protect%20cows%2C%20and%20I%20support%20the%20move%20to%20do%20so%2C%20you%20did%20not%20wait%20to%20count%20the%20number%20of%20cows.%20You%20just%20went%20and%20built%20the%20cow%20shelters.%20Are%20we%20women%20any%20less%20that%20you%20have%20to%20wait%20to%20count%20the%20numbers%20and%20draw%20lines%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20need%20is%20direct%20action.%20Honourable%20PM%20this%20is%20your%20moment%20to%20show%20us%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20hai%20toh%20mumkin%20hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Implement%20the%20Bill%20immediately%20based%20on%20today%E2%80%99s%20voter%E2%80%99s%20list%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDemanding%20a%20timeline%20from%20the%20government%2C%20RSP%E2%80%99s%20N.K.%20Premachandran%20asked%20what%20was%20the%20need%20for%20a%20special%20session%20if%20the%20Bill%20was%20not%20going%20to%20be%20implemented%20any%20time%20soon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20prevented%20this%20government%20from%20introducing%20this%20Bill%20in%20the%20last%20nine-and-a-half%20years%20%5Bthat%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20in%20power%5D%3F%20The%20delay%20has%20to%20be%20explained.%20I%20would%20also%20like%20to%20seek%20assurance%20over%20when%20the%20government%20is%20planning%20on%20implementing%20this%20Bill%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajiv%20Ranjan%20Singh%2C%20JDU%20MP%20said%20that%20the%20Bill%20was%20an%20election%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejumla%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%202024.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202014%2C%20they%20misled%20the%20unemployed%20in%20this%20country%20by%20promising%20jobs%20to%202%20crore%20people%20and%20promised%20to%20bring%20back%20black%20money%20and%20give%20Rs%2015-20%20lakh%20to%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20poor.%20This%20time%20they%20want%20to%20mislead%20the%20women.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsonia-gandhi-womens-reservation-debate-congress-renewed-energy%5C%22%3EChoosing%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20To%20Lead%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Debate%20Shows%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Renewed%20Energy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOBC%2C%20Muslims%20and%20the%20Quota%20within%20Quota%20Question%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20debate%20also%20saw%20the%20oppositon%20MPs%20reiterating%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20sub-quota%20based%20on%20caste.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsonia-gandhi-womens-reservation-debate-congress-renewed-energy%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOpening%20the%20debate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20opposition%2C%20former%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93%20while%20supporting%20the%20Bill%20%E2%80%93%20demanded%20on%20behalf%20of%20her%20party%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20should%20also%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census%20to%20accommodate%20women%20from%20the%20Dalit%2C%20Adivasi%2C%20and%20OBC%20communities%20within%20the%2033%25%20quota.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20demand%20is%20that%20this%20Bill%20be%20enforced%20immediately%2C%20along%20with%20caste%20census%20to%20facilitate%20reservation%20for%20women%20belonging%20to%20scheduled%20castes%2C%20scheduled%20tribes%2C%20and%20other%20backward%20classes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20and%20the%20need%20to%20make%20separate%20provisions%20for%20SC%2FST%20and%20OBC%20women%20was%20also%20raised%20by%20other%20Congress%20MPs%2C%20JD(U)%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20RLP%2C%20and%20BSP%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnti-Muslim%2C%20anti-OBC%3A%20Owaisi%20opposes%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAIMIM%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%2C%20while%20opposing%20the%20Bill%2C%20said%20that%20the%20legislation%20was%20anti-Muslim%20and%20anti-OBC%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20justification%20(behind%20this%20Bill)%20is%20to%20bring%20more%20women%20to%20parliament.%20Why%20is%20that%20justification%20not%20being%20extended%20to%20Muslim%20and%20OBC%20women%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Modi%20government%20wants%20to%20increase%20representation%20for%20savarna%20women%20and%20not%20OBC%20women.%20690%20women%20have%20been%20elected%20till%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20%E2%80%93%20out%20of%20this%2C%20only%2025%20have%20come%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20May%20I%20tell%20you%2C%20sir%2C%20that%20this%20number%20has%20never%20gone%20beyond%20four.%20When%20I%20hear%20that%20reservation%20cannot%20be%20given%20on%20religious%20grounds%2C%20you%20are%20deceiving%20the%20Muslim%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%20statement%20was%20in%20reference%20to%20Union%20minister%20for%20women%20and%20child%20development%20Smriti%20Irani%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20statement%20that%20reservations%20cannot%20be%20provided%20on%20religious%20grounds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPM%20says%20I%20am%20an%20OBC%20but%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20look%20after%20the%20OBC%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Owaisi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20sort%20of%20vandana%20is%20when%20Bilkis%20Bano%E2%80%99s%20rapists%20are%20released%3F%2063%20million%20women%20have%20disappeared%20and%2022%20million%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20workforce.%20This%20is%20a%20women%E2%80%99s%20deception%20Bill.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20inclusive%20Bill.%20It%20is%20an%20exclusive%20Bill%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F30185604%2FFij69mfVIAMVzO0.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F30185604%2FFij69mfVIAMVzO0.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F30185604%2FFij69mfVIAMVzO0-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F30185604%2FFij69mfV