bate%20on%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20%E2%80%93%20or%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Her%20intervention%20on%20Wednesday%20(September%2020)%20after%20a%20long%20gap%20was%20striking%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20mounted%20an%20earnest%20criticism%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20tie%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhistoric-day-says-pm-modi-as-he-announces-womens-reservation-bill-in-new-parliament%5C%22%3Ereservation%20for%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20legislatures%20to%20a%20census%20and%20then%20a%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies.%20The%202021%20census%2C%20delayed%20initially%20by%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20has%20been%20postponed%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20because%20of%20which%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20delimitation%20cannot%20be%20taken%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSpeaker%20sir%2C%20%5Bthe%5D%20Congress%20supports%20the%20Bill.%20We%20are%20happy%20to%20have%20the%20Bill%20passed%20but%20are%20also%20worried.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20a%20question.%20For%20over%2013%20years%2C%20Indian%20women%20have%20waited%20to%20take%20their%20political%20responsibility%2C%20and%20now%20they%20are%20being%20told%20to%20wait%20for%20some%20more%20years.%20How%20many%20years%2C%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20%E2%80%93%20two%20years%2C%20four%20years%2C%20six%20years%2C%20eight%20years%3F%20Is%20such%20a%20treatment%20towards%20Indian%20women%20appropriate%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20perhaps%20buoyed%20by%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20shown%20a%20renewed%20resolve%20to%20sharpen%20its%20responses%20and%20stances%20to%20combat%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20public%20relations%20overdrive%20on%20significant%20issues.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20has%20also%20fielded%20its%20leaders%20strategically%20to%20take%20on%20issues%20for%20which%20they%20are%20best%20suited%20at%20a%20given%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20buoyancy%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20swift%20decisions%20taken%20by%20party%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20ever%20since%20he%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20top%20position.%20These%20include%20the%20show%20of%20organisational%20cohesiveness%20and%20unequivocal%20political%20messaging%20in%20the%20recent%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20meeting%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20looking%20different%20and%20responding%20differently%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20while%20asking%20pertinent%20questions%20to%20the%20government%2C%20recalled%20how%20her%20husband%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20first%20moved%20a%20Constitutional%20Amendment%20Bill%20to%20reserve%20seats%20for%20women%20in%20the%20local%20governments.%20The%20move%20was%20defeated%20by%20seven%20votes%2C%20she%20said%20but%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20P.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao-led%20Congress%20government%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20averred%20that%20because%20of%20such%20continued%20discussions%20spanning%20over%20three%20decades%2C%20on%20the%20important%20issue%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20in%20parliament%20and%20assemblies%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20parties%20have%20come%20around%20to%20support%20the%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20she%20also%20demanded%20on%20behalf%20of%20her%20party%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20should%20also%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census%20to%20accommodate%20women%20from%20the%20Dalit%2C%20Adivasi%2C%20and%20OBC%20communities%20within%20the%2033%25%20quota%20under%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20speaks%20of%20the%20consciousness%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20after%20remaining%20in%20power%20for%20over%20nine%20years%20may%20be%20an%20instrument%20to%20get%20leverage%20over%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20consistent%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20clamour%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20has%20only%20grown%20ahead%20of%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%20in%20five%20states%20%E2%80%93%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20and%20Mizoram%20%E2%80%93%20as%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20have%20come%20together%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%20brings%20a%20moral%20certitude%20to%20the%20debate%2C%20as%20she%20is%20among%20those%20rare%20political%20leaders%20who%20have%20unequivocally%20supported%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20every%20time%20it%20was%20discussed%20or%20tabled%20in%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%20By%20placing%20Gandhi%20to%20lead%20the%20party%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20shown%20strategic%20thinking%20on%20its%20part%2C%20as%20even%20her%20opponents%20will%20swear%20by%20her%20commitment%20to%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20recalling%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20last%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20in%202010%2C%20Brinda%20Karat%2C%20a%20politburo%20member%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fbrinda-karat-salute-women-women-reservation-bill-8947284%2F%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20highlighting%20not%20merely%20a%20BJP%20leader%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20thwart%20the%20safe%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill%20in%202010%20but%20also%20Sonia%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20honesty%20on%20the%20reservation%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20Bill%20was%20adopted%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%20March%202010%20under%20the%20UPA%20government%2C%20I%20was%20an%20active%20participant%20in%20the%20discussions%20and%20a%20witness%20to%20the%20shenanigans%20of%20various%20players.%20One%20of%20the%20issues%20raised%20in%20the%20discussions%20in%20the%20Chairman%E2%80%99s%20chamber%20by%20a%20BJP%20leader%20was%20that%20a%20condition%20for%20passage%20must%20be%20%E2%80%9Corder%20in%20the%20House%E2%80%9D.%20It%20seemed%20to%20me%20that%20this%20was%20a%20green%20signal%20to%20those%20who%20had%20already%20planned%20for%20%E2%80%9Cdisorder%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20House%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20Bill%20was%20not%20adopted%20and%20that%20the%20credit%20should%20not%20go%20to%20the%20UPA%20government.%20There%20were%20those%20in%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20too%2C%20who%20were%20not%20keen%2C%20including%20a%20top%20leader%20who%20was%20in%20discussions%20with%20other%20constituents%20of%20the%20UPA%20on%20the%20issue.%20But%20the%20unequivocal%20support%20for%20the%20Bill%20of%20the%20then%20UPA%20chairperson%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20ensured%20that%20the%20various%20plans%20being%20hatched%20to%20once%20again%20sabotage%20the%20Bill%20were%20blocked.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20firm%20position%20taken%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairperson%20Hamid%20Ansari%20was%20a%20critical%20factor%20in%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill.%20An%20SP%20member%20sitting%20just%20behind%20me%20smashed%20a%20glass%2C%20cut%20his%20hand%20and%2C%20dripping%20blood%2C%20leapt%20onto%20the%20table%20protesting%20against%20the%20Bill.%20Many%20others%20opposing%20the%20Bill%20were%20loud%20and%20noisy.%20The%20unfazed%20Chairperson%20had%20all%20these%20gentlemen%20removed%20without%20further%20ado%2C%20the%20House%20was%20brought%20to%20order%20and%20the%20Bill%20adopted.%20A%20historic%20moment.%20When%20we%20walked%20out%20into%20the%20cool%20night%20air%2C%20there%20stood%20a%20beaming%20Sushma%20Swaraj%2C%20then%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20waiting%20for%20us.%20She%20hugged%20me%20and%20women%20MPs%20across%20party%20lines%20celebrated%20together.%20It%20was%20a%20wonderful%20example%20of%20joining%20hands%20for%20a%20bigger%20cause%2C%20so%20lacking%20today%20among%20the%20women%20leaders%20and%20ministers%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20note%20that%20Karat%E2%80%99s%20party%20had%20by%202010%20withdrawn%20its%20support%20to%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh-led%20UPA%20government%20and%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20the%20fiercest%20critics%20of%20the%20UPA.%20Yet%2C%20that%20did%20not%20prevent%20her%20from%20acknowledging%20the%20role%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20as%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20advocates%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20in%20parliament%20and%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20demanding%20a%20sub-quota%20for%20the%20Dalit%2C%20Adivasi%2C%20and%20OBC%20communities%20within%20the%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20representatives%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20brought%20itself%20closer%20to%20its%20INDIA%20allies%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20the%20Congress%20failed%20to%20muster%20enough%20numbers%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20only%20because%20of%20the%20opposition%20from%20the%20Mandal%20parties%20that%20were%20demanding%20this%20sub-quota.%20However%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20among%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20has%20allowed%20the%20Congress%20to%20formulate%20a%20collective%20position%20on%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill.%20A%20number%20of%20non-Congress%20leaders%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20have%20also%20acknowledged%2C%20although%20privately%2C%20the%20flexibility%20that%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20and%20especially%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93%20has%20shown%20on%20different%20issues%20to%20accommodate%20the%20common%20interests%20of%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%