3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20informs%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20club%20of%20school-going%20girls%20from%20Class%206%20to%2012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20female%20teacher%20is%20appointed%20as%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20club.%20In%20addition%2C%20a%20female%20student%20is%20appointed%20as%20the%20convenor%20who%20keeps%20track%20of%20the%20female%20students%E2%80%99%20attendance%20in%20their%20classes.%20If%20a%20girl%20is%20absent%20for%20more%20than%20a%20week%2C%20she%20reports%20about%20it%20to%20the%20chairman.%20On%20learning%20this%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%20%3C%2Fem%3Erepresentatives%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Evisit%20the%20absentee%E2%80%99s%20house%20to%20enquire%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saju.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20learn%20that%20the%20family%20is%20forcing%20the%20girl%20to%20get%20married%2C%20they%20try%20to%20convince%20the%20family%20to%20get%20her%20back%20to%20school%20citing%20legal%20complications%20of%20the%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20the%20administration%20has%20formed%20WhatsApp%20groups%20of%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20representatives%2C%20women%20school%20management%20committees%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Childline%2C%20child%20welfare%20committees%2C%20and%20district-level%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20WhatsApp%20group%2C%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20representatives%20inform%20the%20group%20members%20about%20the%20case.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20parents%20are%20not%20convinced%2C%20then%20administrative%20support%20is%20sought.%20This%20is%20when%20our%20second%20layer%20of%20officials%20comes%20into%20the%20picture.%20It%20comprises%20a%20one-stop%20centre%20(where%20young%20girls%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20experts%20for%20counselling)%2C%20a%20district%20child%20protection%20unit%2C%20counsellors%2C%20psychologists%2C%20and%20legal%20practitioners%20who%20reach%20out%20to%20families%20to%20convince%20them.%20Most%20of%20the%20cases%20get%20resolved%20in%20the%20second%20layer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20Tripura%2C%2040.1%20percent%20of%20women%20aged%2020%E2%80%9324%20years%20were%20married%20before%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330400%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20Tripura%2C%2040.1%20percent%20of%20women%20aged%2020%E2%80%9324%20years%20are%20married%20before%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20the%20families%20start%20questioning%20our%20rights%20to%20prevent%20the%20marriage%2C%20we%20activate%20our%20third%20layer.%20My%20sub-divisional%20magistrate%20rushes%20to%20the%20spot%20and%20tells%20the%20parents%20that%20the%20administration%20shall%20file%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20family%20as%20child%20marriage%20is%20a%20punishable%20offence.%20But%20even%20then%2C%20if%20families%20go%20ahead%2C%20we%20send%20police%20officers%20to%20their%20homes%20and%20register%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20family.%20We%20then%20get%20an%20affidavit%20signed%20by%20the%20parents%20stating%20that%20they%E2%80%99ll%20not%20marry%20off%20their%20daughters%20until%20they%20are%2018%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20collector.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20timely%20intervention%2C%20Saju%20has%20been%20able%20to%20prevent%2090%20planned%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20district%20in%20the%20past%20year%20with%20the%20help%20of%20158%20school%20clubs%20across%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20work%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20if%20we%20are%20able%20to%20continue%20this%20way%20for%20another%20year%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20eradicate%20child%20marriages%20in%20our%20district.%20Seeing%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20work%2C%20the%20state%20government%20aims%20to%20expand%20this%20initiative%20across%20Tripura.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20work%20is%20deeply%20satisfying%20to%20me%20because%20when%20these%20girls%20talk%20to%20me%2C%20I%20realise%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20preventing%20marriages%3B%20we%E2%80%99re%20saving%20lives.%20These%20young%20girls%20now%20have%20a%20platform%20to%20voice%20their%20concerns.%20While%20I%E2%80%99m%20involved%20in%20various%20other%20development%20projects%2C%20this%20one%20is%20particularly%20dear%20to%20me.%20I%20believe%20it%20will%20ensure%20a%20better%20future%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saju.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Saju%20Vaheed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695218864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tripura%20is%20notorious%20for%20child%20marriages%20with%20four%20in%2010%20girls%20getting%20married%20before%20turning%2018.%20In%20a%20novel%20approach%2C%20South%20Tripura%20District%20Magistrate%20Saju%20Vaheed%20revived%20%E2%80%98Balika%20Manch%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20school%20club%20cum%20platform%20to%20prevent%20young%20girls%20from%20dropping%20out%20of%20school%20and%20getting%20married.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330387%2Fias-officer-district-magistrate-saju-vaheed-balika-manch-prevent-child-marriage-south-tripura%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Even%20Doctors%20Who%20Have%20Scored%20No%20Marks%20in%20NEET%20PG%20Can%20Now%20Become%20Specialists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F12151524%2Fdoctor-563428_1920.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20move%20that%20is%20ostensibly%20meant%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20postgraduate%20medical%20seat%20remains%20vacant%20but%20will%20in%20practice%20benefit%20private%20colleges%2C%20the%20health%20ministry%20has%20announced%20that%20even%20a%20candidate%20who%20has%20not%20scored%20any%20marks%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0or%20even%20those%20who%20scored%20negative%20marks%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0will%20be%20eligible%20for%20NEET%20PG%20counselling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFordaIndia%2Fstatus%2F1704411852028170610%5C%22%3Ewelcomed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20some%20doctors%E2%80%99%20associations%20like%20the%20Federation%20of%20Resident%20Doctors%20in%20India%20(FORDA).%20Still%2C%20it%20was%20also%20opposed%20by%20other%20associations%20and%20individual%20doctors%2C%20who%20felt%20that%20the%20move%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmockery%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20standard%20of%20medical%20education%20and%20the%20healthcare%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20doctor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrRohanKrishna3%2Fstatus%2F1704425699187237128%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20reducing%20the%20cut-off%20to%20zero%20percentile%20will%20encourage%20corruption%20and%20high%20fees%20in%20private%20medical%20colleges%20and%20would%20put%20the%20medical%20industry%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20sale%E2%80%9D%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EI%20completely%20disagree%20with%20the%20bizarre%20circular%20released%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMoHFW_INDIA%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MoHFW_INDIA%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20removing%20cut%20off%20bar%20from%23NEETPG.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPMOIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40PMOIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20only%20going%20to%20promote%20corruption%20and%20high%20fee%20in%20pvt%20medical%20colleges.%20%3Cbr%3EIt%20is%20Shameful%20tht%20any%20medical%20body%20supported%20this%20step%20of%20zero%20percent%20merit.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Femv6crDBYw%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Femv6crDBYw%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20Rohan%20Krishnan%20(%40DrRohanKrishna3)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrRohanKrishna3%2Fstatus%2F1704425699187237128%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20minimum%20qualifying%20score%20for%20NEET%20PG%20was%2050%20percentile%20for%20general%20category%20students%20%E2%80%93%20meaning%20that%20a%20candidate%20must%20score%20better%20than%2050%25%20of%20the%20total%20candidates%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20test.%20After%20qualification%2C%20the%20candidates%20would%20choose%20seats%20in%20different%20departments%20based%20on%20cutoff%20scores%20and%20the%20availability%20of%20seats%20in%20each%20specialty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20has%20now%20been%20reduced%20to%20zero%20percentile%20across%20all%20categories%20%E2%80%93%20meaning%20there%20is%20no%20cut-off%20at%20all.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdnbbsr.s3waas.gov.in%2Fs3e0f7a4d0ef9b84b83b693bbf3feb8e6e%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F2023092040.pdf%5C%22%3Enotification%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Medical%20Counselling%20Committee%20of%20India%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20for%20the%20information%20to%20candidates%20that%20vide%20Letter%20No.%20U-12021%2F07%2F2023-MEC%20(Pt-I)%20dated%2020.09.2023%20(Copy%20attached%20below)%2C%20the%20qualifying%20percentile%20for%20PG%20Courses%20(Medical%2F%20Dental)%20for%20NEET%20PG%20Counselling%202023%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20%E2%80%98ZERO%E2%80%99%20across%20all%20categories%20by%20MoHFW.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20this%20regard%2C%20it%20is%20mentioned%20that%20Fresh%20Registration%20%26amp%3B%20Choice%20Filling%20for%20Round-3%20of%20PG%20Counselling%20will%20be%20opened%20again%20for%20candidates%20who%20have%20become%20eligible%20after%20reduction%20of%20percentile.%20Candidates%20who%20have%20become%20freshly%20eligible%20can%20register%20and%20participate%20in%20Round-3%20of%20counselling.%20The%20candidates%20who%20are%20already%20registered%20need%20not%20register%20again.%20However%2C%20they%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20edit%20their%20choices.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20fresh%20schedule%20for%20Round-3%20onwards%20for%20PG%20Counselling%20will%20be%20put%20up%20on%20MCC%20website%20soon.%20Candidates%20are%20advised%20to%20be%20in%20touch%20with%20MCC%20website%20for%20further%20updates.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20week%2C%20associations%20like%20FORDA%20and%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20had%20written%20to%20the%20health%20ministry%20to%20lower%20the%20cut-off.%20The%20IMA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIMAIndiaOrg%2Fstatus%2F1701906192313033168%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20move%20will%20ensure%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpostgraduate%20programs%20in%20various%20medical%20colleges%20across%20the%20country%20and%20not%20a%20single%20postgraduate%20seat%20goes%20vacant%E2%80%9D.%20Meanwhile%2C%20FORDA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffordaindia%2Fstatus%2F1702662854149853496%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20would%20%E2%80%9Cprovide%20a%20lifeline%20to%20numerous%20medical%20students%20who%20are%20in%20a%20state%20of%20flux%20due%20to%20these%20uncertainties%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20other%20doctors%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20after%20two%20rounds%20of%20NEET%20PG%20counselling%2C%20most%20of%20the%20seats%20that%20were%20left%20vacant%20were%20in%20private%20colleges.%20This%20is%20not%20because%20there%20are%20no%20eligible%20candidates%2C%20but%20because%20most%20private%20colleges%20charge%20fees%20that%20are%20unaffordable%20for%20a%20large%20number%20of%20applicants%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20J.A.%20Jayalal%2C%20a%20former%20IMA%20president%2C%20called%20the%20announcement%20%E2%80%9Cdisastrous%E2%80%9D%20and%20will%20destablise%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20disastrous%20to%20know%20announcement%20by%20the%20MOH%20on%20NEET%20PG%20eligibility%20mark%20as%20Zero.%20why%20the%20hell%20you%20conducted%20the%20exam%3F%20Why%20do%20you%20want%20to%20destabilise%20medicine%20%3F%20Convert%20all%20lapsed%20seats%20as%20Govt%20seat%2C%20in%20no%20time%20all%20seats%20will%20be%20filled%20up%20by%20meritorious%20students%20.%20Shame%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fdkxv8e3mj1%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fdkxv8e3mj1%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Prof.%20Dr.%20J.A.%20Jayalal%20(%40jayalal10)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjayalal10%2Fstatus%2F1704457961224249833%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDoctors%20who%20opposed%20the%20reduction%20in%20cut-off%20said%20that%20if%20the%20vacant%20seats%20were%20%E2%80%9Cconverted%E2%80%9D%20into%20government%20college%20seats%2C%20they%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjayalal10%2Fstatus%2F1704457961224249833%5C%22%3Efilled%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20without%20the%20need%20to%20reduce%20the%20percentile.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20said%20that%20the%20reduction%20of%20the%20cut-off%20to%20zero%20percentile%20will%20ensure%20that%20candidates%20who%20have%20scored%20low%20marks%20can%20effectively%20%E2%80%9Cbuy%E2%80%9D%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E5%20Step%20guide%20to%20meritocracy%20%3Cbr%3E1.%20Charge%202%20Crores%2B%20fees.%3Cbr%3E2.%20Make%20it%20unaffordable%20for%2099%25%20Indians.%20%3Cbr%3E3.%20Declare%20vacant%20seats%3Cbr%3E4.%20Force%20NMC%20to%20lower%20eligibility%20to%20fill%20vacant%20seats.%20%3Cbr%3E5.%20Get%20rich%20brats%20with%20ZERO%20merit%20to%20grab%20those%20vacat%20seats.%3Cbr%3EHigh%20fees%20is%20Reservation%20for%20the%20rich!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FU63UAASvtb%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FU63UAASvtb%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Maheshwer%20Peri%20(%40maheshperi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmaheshperi%2Fstatus%2F1704473685938287039%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWe%20are%20shocked%20to%20see%20such%20notice%20released%20by%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20regarding%20NEET%20PG%20Cut%20off.%3Cbr%3EIt%20is%20ridiculous%20to%20see%20zero%20percentile%20candidates%20are%20eligible%20for%20getting%20a%20Postgraduate%20Seat.%3Cbr%3EThis%20is%20mockery%20of%20the%20standard%20of%20Medical%20Education%20%26amp%3B%20healthcare%20system%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrRohanKrishna3%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40DrRohanKrishna3%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FkyNfoRJFmd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FkyNfoRJFmd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20FAIMA%20Doctors%20Association%20(%40FAIMA_INDIA_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFAIMA_INDIA_%2Fstatus%2F1704429054320168987%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFor%20becoming%20a%20specialist%20doctor%20in%20India%20you%20need%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FZERO%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ZERO%3C%2Fa%3E%20percentile%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FNEET%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23NEET%3C%2Fa%3E%20PG%20.%20MONEY%20hai%20to%20honey%20hai%20.%20Sad%20state%20of%20Indian%20medical%20education.%3Cbr%3EIf%20SEATS%20remains%20vacant%20even%20after%20round%203%20counseling%20then%20convert%20them%20into%20govt%20seats%20trust%20me%20Not%20even%20a%20single%20seat%20will%20remain%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fav6oDJLWxy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fav6oDJLWxy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dr%20Manoj%20Chaudhary%20(%40MK_Chaudhary04)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMK_Chaudhary04%2Fstatus%2F1704448263972401256%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIndeed%20Black%20day%20for%20Medical%20field%E2%80%A6%20Candidates%20not%20qualifing%20will%20become%20a%20Specialist%20doctors%20buy%20paying%20handsome%20amount%20of%20money%20to%20Deemed%20University%20and%20Pvt%20Colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dr.Darshil%20Khared%20%E2%9D%81%20(%40darshil_khared)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdarshil_khared%2Fstatus%2F1704417477080613287%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EQualifying%20percentile%20for%20NEET%20PG%20being%20zero%20is%20absurd.%20One%20has%20to%20just%20appear%20for%20the%20exam%20and%20leave%20it%20all%20blank.%20I%20am%20really%20hoping%20this%20is%20some%20kind%20of%20fake%20news.%20Imagine%20the%20rich%20abusing%20this%2C%20just%20appear%2C%20pay%20crores%20and%20get%20a%20seat%20in%20a%20private%20college%20all%20without%20a%20bare%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20Anuj%20(%40anujtiwari11)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanujtiwari11%2Fstatus%2F1704481164948353495%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695218458000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F12151524%2Fdoctor-563428_1920.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fneet-pg-cut-off-zero-percentile-health-ministry%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20health%20ministry%20on%20Wednesday%20issued%20a%20notification%20reducing%20the%20cut-off%20for%20NEET%20PG%20to%20zero%20percentile.%20The%20move%20will%20benefit%20private%20colleges%20that%20charge%20exorbitant%20fees%2C%20critics%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A79%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fneet-pg-cut-off-zero-percentile-health-ministry%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Startup%20Will%20Help%20You%20Find%20Less%20Crowded%20Fuel%20Stations%2C%20For%20CNG%20%26amp%3B%20EVs%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20got%20his%20licence%20at%2018%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20tried%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306067%2Fcollege-dropout-launches-ev-startup-builds-made-in-india-luxury-electric-suv-pravaig%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edriving%20a%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20every%20other%20person.%20However%2C%20he%20would%20often%20end%20up%20getting%20into%20accidents%2C%20and%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20other%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20stop%20driving.%20This%20made%20him%20a%20regular%20user%20of%20cab%20services%20like%20Ola%20and%20Uber.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20decision%20to%20stay%20off%20the%20roads%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20startup%20idea%20which%20aimed%20to%20decongest%20fuel%20stations%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Vaibhav%2C%20an%20engineer%20from%20BITS%20Pilani%2C%20was%20doing%20an%20internship%20in%20Greater%20Noida.%20During%20the%20half-hour%20commute%20between%20his%20home%20and%20office%2C%20he%20used%20to%20strike%20up%20conversations%20with%20cab%20drivers.%20They%20mainly%20drove%20CNG%20vehicles%20and%20this%20is%20where%20he%20learnt%20about%20their%20biggest%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20drivers%20complained%20of%20one%20single%20problem%20%E2%80%93%20the%20line%20at%20the%20fuel%20station%20was%20very%20long.%20Out%20of%20the%2010%20hours%20they%20spent%20on%20the%20road%2C%20an%20hour%20was%20wasted%20at%20these%20fuel%20st