172-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330322%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENawgati%20founders%20%E2%80%93%20Aryan%20Sisodia%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20and%20Aalaap%20Nair.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20came%20up%20with%20two%20solutions%2C%20an%20app%20for%20consumers%2C%20and%20its%20flagship%20product%2C%20Aaveg%2C%20a%20B2B%20platform%2C%20for%20fuel%20companies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20improve%20compliance%2C%20achieve%20operational%20efficiency%2C%20monitor%20real-time%20congestion%2C%20and%20direct%20customers%20to%20less%20crowded%20stations%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAaveg%20is%20a%20single%20point%20of%20reference%20for%20fuel%20station%20owners%20to%20have%20complete%20oversight%20of%20transit%2C%20waiting%20and%20serving%20time%2C%20attendants%20deployed%2C%20and%20under%20or%20over-utilisation%20of%20resources.%20We%20help%20fuel%20companies%20and%2For%20dealers%20with%20congestion%20management%2C%20compliance%20monitoring%2C%20and%20automating%20forecourt%20operations%2C%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20scale%20up%20or%20scale%20down%20operations%20at%20any%20outlet%20and%20make%20decisions%20backed%20by%20data%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aryan%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CTO%20at%20Nawgati.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Aaveg%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20Sanskrit%20for%20impulse%2C%20is%20built%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296093%2Fcouple-converts-tempo-traveller-into-caravan-to-travel-van-life-youtube%2F%5