e%20insights%20regarding%20the%20challenges%20encountered%20by%20the%20teams%20at%20CNG%20stations.%20We%20then%20made%20some%20changes%20to%20enhance%20Aaveg%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Aryan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20pilot%2C%20IGL%20signed%20an%20annual%20contract%20with%20Nawgati.%20Today%2C%20Aaveg%20is%20live%20at%20IGL%2C%20Indian%20Oil%20outlets%20in%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Mahanagar%20Gas%20(MGL)%20outlets%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20GAIL%20Gas%2C%20Torrent%20Gas%2C%20JioBP%2C%20HP%20Gas%20among%20several%20other%20fuel%20companies%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20plan%20to%20onboard%2015%2C000%20fueling%20outlets%20within%20two%20years.%20The%20startup%20has%20filed%20a%20patent%20for%20this%20technology%2C%20which%20helps%20fuel%20pumps%20manage%20congestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20Nawgati%20helps%20consumers%2C%20especially%20cab%20drivers%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nawgati%20app%20helps%20consumers%20find%20nearest%20fuel%20stations%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-170x300.jpg%20170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-500x883.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-768x1356.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-870x1536.jpg%20870w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-150x265.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20c