e.%20He%20woke%20up%20at%204%20am%20to%20help%20his%20parents%20at%20their%20snack%2Ftea%20shop.%20After%20returning%20from%20college%2C%20he%20worked%20at%20the%20shop%20till%2011%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20a%20small%20village%20in%20the%20southernmost%20part%20of%20India%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20the%20Northeastern%20state%20in%20search%20of%20a%20better%20life%20for%20his%20family.%20And%20he%20succeeded%20in%20his%20goals.%20Today%2C%20he%20lives%20in%20a%202%2C000-square-foot%2C%20four-bedroom%20house.%20He%20also%20supported%20his%20three%20younger%20siblings%E2%80%99%20education%20and%20marriage%2C%20making%20his%20parents%E2%80%99%20lives%20comfortable.%20He%20credits%20all%20his%20achievements%20to%20his%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20made%20sure%20that%20he%20gave%20all%20of%20us%20a%20good%20education.%20He%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20educate%20us%20and%20managed%20to%20pay%20all%20our%20fees%20by%20borrowing%20money%20and%20mortgaging%20jewellery.%20Three%20of%20my%20siblings%20are%20postgraduates%20and%20one%20has%20completed%20her%20doctorate.%20All%20of%20us%20are%20in%20good%20positions%20thanks%20to%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20insistence%20on%20getting%20us%20educated%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nellayapan%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20humble%20beginnings%20to%20deputy%20director%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nellayapan%20B%2C%20OSD%20to%20Nagaland%20Chief%20Minister%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%