20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20become%20the%20school%20principal%20in%202012%20and%20continued%20working%20there%20till%202017.%20Then%2C%20in%202018%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20assistant%20director%20at%20the%20Directorate%20of%20School%20Education%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20he%20was%20promoted%20to%20the%20role%20of%20deputy%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20trailblazer%20in%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20640px)%20100vw%2C%20640px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nellayapan%20B's%20family%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnellayapan-family-1695049875-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330247%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAll%20of%20Nellayapan%E2%80%99s%20siblings%20are%20well-educated%20due%20to%20their%20father%E2%80%99s%20efforts%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20COVID%20hit%20the%20nation%2C%20Nagaland%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20states%20to%20embrace%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322755%2Fkarnataka-divaa-uthkarsha-project-surya-type-one-diabetes-awareness-for-underprivileged-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20even%20recognised%20by%20the%20Organisation%20for%20Economic%20Co-operation%20and%20Development%20Education%20(OECD).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202020%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20School%20Education%20rolled%20out%20a%20tele%2Fonline%20education%20programme%20through%20which%20education%20was%20offered%20through%20TV%20(Doordarshan%2C%20Kohima)%20and%20radio%20(All%20India%20Radio%2C%20Kohima).%20In%20May%202020%2C%20they%20also%20offered%20educational%20content%20through%20a%20YouTube%20channel.%20This%20programme%20was%20led%20by%20C%20Shanavas%20%E2%80%94%20principal%20director%20of%20school%20education%20%E2%80%94%20and%20supported%20by%20Nellayapan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHeartiest%20congratulations%20to%20the%20awardees%20of%20Governor's%20Gold%20Medal%20and%20Governor's%20Commendation%20Certificate%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2F74th_IndependenceDay%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%2374th_IndependenceDay%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqdEbUZl7OP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqdEbUZl7OP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Neiphiu%20Rio%20(%40Neiphiu_Rio)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNeiphiu_Rio%2Fstatus%2F1294503464827944962%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2015%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20hilly%20areas%20in%20the%20state%20face%20network%20issues.%20So%20we%20ironed%20out%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20reach%20every%20student%2C%20irrespective%20of%20network.%20We%20were%20also%20the%20first%20state%20to%20conduct%20online%20exams%20for%20students%20from%20Classes%205%E2%80%9312%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nellayapan%2C%20who%20was%20awarded%20the%20Governor%E2%80%99s%20commendation