miserable%20condition.%20Also%2C%20there%20are%20chances%20that%20their%20decaying%20bodies%20could%20spread%20diseases%20and%20threaten%20human%20and%20environmental%20health%20alike%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoved%20deeply%20by%20this%20incident%2C%20Manjit%20converted%20his%20bicycle%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98bird%20ambulance%E2%80%99.%20With%20this%2C%20he%20has%20treated%201%2C160%20birds%20so%20far.%20He%20even%20ensures%20that%20birds%20who%20die%20are%20given%20a%20proper%20burial%2C%20totalling%20to%201%2C280%20avians%20like%20pigeons%2C%20crows%2C%20parrots%2C%20and%20turtle%20doves%20in%20Chandigarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERefused%20Bank%20Job%20for%20Environment%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20BA%20dropout%2C%20Manjit%20initially%20worked%20as%20a%20drawing%20teacher%20in%20a%20private%20school.%20Through%20the%20school%2C%20he%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20same%20local%20NGO%20that%20motivated%20him%20to%20do%20social%20work.%20Then%2C%20to%20do%20his%20bit%20to%20reduce%20the%20rising%20air%20pollution%2C%20Manjit%20switched%20to%20riding%20a%20bicycle%20in%201990%20at%20the%20age%20of%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201999%2C%20after%20his%20marriage%2C%20Manjit%20quit%20his%20job%20at%20the%20school%20to%20dedicate%20himself%20entirely%20to%20the%20environment.%20As%20a%20side%20hustle%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20painter%2C%20but%20his%20in-laws%20were%20concerned.%20They%2C%20however%2C%20managed%20to%20get%20him%20a%20job%20offer%20as%20a%20bank%20clerk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20job%20offered%20me%20triple%20the%20income%20from%20what%20I%20was%20earning.%20But%20I%20had%20to%20refuse%20it.%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20get%20trapped%20in%20a%20regular%20job%20in%20a%20corporate%20world%20where%20I%20would%20have%20to%20compromise%20on%20my%20mission%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%